Pa in chhuahsan turin a ko :-
Abrahama tana Pa in chhuahsan ngei tur chu a pa, amah hringtu Tera in, an chhungkua bik chu a ni. Keini tan vet hung chuan mahni (self) chhuahsan a ni.. Kan pa chu Diabola a ni a, Diabola in chhuhsan tak takna chu mahni (self) thihsan ngei hi a ni. Ka tana hmelma thi har ber chu keimah a ni a, i tan chuan nangmah kha a ni.. Mahni inthihsan lotu chu Thlarau Thianghlim khatin a awm theih loh. Mahni thihsan tih awmzia hian hnuk chat leh marphu chawl lam thu a kawk lo va, mahnia ro inrel thin (Sovereignty of self) kha paih thlak dera awmin Thlarau Thianghlim rorelna hnuai (Sovereignty of Holy Spirit) ah a intulut ta tihna a ni.
Kan pianphung reng rengah mahni inhmangaihnaa khat mihring kan ni a, mahni inhmangaih luat avanga hlim pawh hlim thei lo hial kan ni tlat tih hi mahni inbum chawp lova awi chi a ni. Chu mahni ringawt inhre ran mai (self centered) chu Krista lalna (Christ centred) chuan a rawn thlak ta tihna a ni. Mahni inphat fel thlapin Abrahama chuan amah kotu Pathian, mita hmuh theih loh (Invisible God) chu a zui a ni. Kan Lalpa Isua pawhin, “Tupawh ka hnenah lokal chuan, a pa te, a nu te, a nupui te, a fa te, a farnu te, ama nun nen lam a huat loh chuan ka zirtir a ni thei lovang,” (LK. 14 : 26-27) a ti a ni. Hemi mahni inphat nun han sawi hian mi thenkhat ten insumna (self control) lam zawngin an la duh hle. Chu lam chu ni lovin Thlarau Thianghlim hnathawh (Holy Spirit control) zara lo awm Thlarau Thianghlim rahchhuah (fruits of Holy Spirit) zawk a ni. Thlarau Thianghlim hnathawh chuan sual simtirin, sual leh a tisualtu a titlawm hlauh zawk a. Insumna mai mai chuan sual a hreng riltam a ni. Naupang thil ruk ching chu a thil rukna leh amah dah hran a ni lo va, tualthattu pawh amah ngei chu hrem a ni. Thlarau Thianghlim hnathawh ril tak mai chuan mahni inpaih thuai duh, thei si lo chu, a chawlhtir hmiah mai a, chumi atang tak chuan Thlarau Thianghlim hnathawh dik tak chuan mihring mihrinna atanga irh chhuak huaisenna a tizam a, mihring huaisenna ni hauh lo Kros thiltihtheihna chuan chhun khah a lo ni thin. Chu huaisenna dik chuan mi dawihzep ber pawh hlauh nei lovin a siam a ni. “Pathian hrin tawh phawt chuan khawvel a ngam zel si a; hei hi a ni khawvel hneha ngamna chu, kan rinna hi. Isua hi Pathian fapa a ni tih ringtu chauh lo chuan tuin nge khawvel ngam thin le?” (Joh. 5 : 4,5). Chutiang chuan Abrahama chuan a pa in ngei pawh chu a chhuahsan fel ta a ni.
Chutichuan Abrahama chu Pathian kohna ang chuan a kal chhuak ta a. A hnenah chuan a nupui leh a neih zawng zawngte, Lot ate an chho ve a. A hnuah chuan Lot ate chhung ngei pawh a then a tul leh ta a. Lot ate chhung nen an inthen fel hnu chuan Pathianin ram tiam chu a kawhhmuh ta a. Pathianin Abrahama hnenah chuan, “Dak la, i awmna atang khan hmar lam te, chhim lam te, chhak lam te, thlang lam te en rawh. I ram hmuh zawng zawng hi nang le hi thlahte, kumkhua atan ka pe dawn che u a ni. Tin, i thlahte chu leia vaivut ang main ka siam ang. Chutichuan mi’n leia vaivut hi an chhiar sen chuan, i thlahte pawh chhiar sen an ni bawk ang,” (Gen. 13 : 14-16) a ti a.
Pathian chuan ram tiam chu a hmuhtir vek a. Nimahsela a luahtu tur atan a chi thlahna kawng a ping (bend) hlauh thung mai. Pathian ram tiam luahna tur chu mihring lama chhuak a ni hauh lo reng a. Ram tiam hmun leh ram tiam luah chu thil dang daih a ni si a. Chi ropui taka awm tura koh a nih laiin a nupui Saraii chu a ching hmiah mai a ni. Pathian thu chuan “Lalpa, Lalpa mi ti nazawng chu van ramah anlut tawp lovang,” a tih angin Thlarau Thianghlim chauh miin Isua hi Lalpa an ti thei thin. “Lalpa Lalpa” tih satliah, hriatna, (mihring hriatna) satliah atanga lo irhchhuak a awm a, Thlarau Thianghlim liau liau-in thinlung chhungril ber atanga Lalpa min tih tirna chu thil danglam daih zu nia. Thlarau ngei chuan kan thlarau hnenah Pathian fate kan ni tih min hriattir thin. Chumi avang chuan Abba (Ka Pa) tia kan au thin hi. A ni, Pathian Chungnungbera chuan ram luah tur min pe duai a, chu ram pek chu luah turin ama hnen atanga chhuak lo chu tun din reng a tum si lo. I neihsa loh Pathian hnen atanga lokal thinlung thar chu i dawng ngei tih i chiang tawh em? Chu ngei chu thutiam fa nihna chu a ni. Chu nunna chu mihring atang rengin a chhuak dawn lo va, a pekte chauh chuan an chang a ni. Pathian thil pek hlu ber Krista chu i saw ii sawi lai le hi duhzia i saw ii sawi lai khan, amah Krista Thlarau chu i hnawl tlat thei si a. Chu Thlarau Thianghlim chu nangmahah lo thleng turin i ngaihdan nghet tlut kha paih phal amg che. Mi tam tak tana kawng dik nia lang, a tawp chu thihna ni si a awm tih chu hre mawlh ang che. Thinlung chhung thlum dep dep khawpin “Ka Pa” tiin Isua chu i ko thei em? “Ka Pa” tiin i ko tawh ngai reng em? Chutiang nun thuruk chui la nei ngai lo a nih ngat chuan zirtirtu ten nangmahah thu an nei reng fo vang. Mangan a hun lai hian mangang rawh. Boralte zawnga chhandam turin Lal Isuan a nunna a pe tawh che, chu chatuan nunna chu chang turin Krista chuan a thlarau thianghlim chu hmangin i thinlung kawngkhar a kik reng si. Mesia (Krista) lokal tur nghakhlela lo thlir tuten an hai angin, ThlarauThianghlim (Krista) chu dingdihlipa lo thlirtuten tunah hian an hai tlat mai. Pathian hnen atanga roluahna kan dawn, keimahni lama chhuak ni lo chu, amah Krista ngeiin a sawi lawk Thlarau Thianghlim chu a ni. (Heb.9 : 14). Thlarau Thianghlim chu tilungngai suh u, tlanna ni atan chuan amahah chhinchhiaha in awm kha, Thlarau Thianghlim chu tivui suh u. Pathian Thlarau Thianghlim chu nangmahniah a awm reng tih in hre lo em ni le? (Ephesi  4 : 30; I Korinth 3 : 16).
Chu Pathian Thlarau Thianghlim chu taksa mita hmuh theih leh khawih theih ni lo, a hnathawh hriat loh theih loh chu kan thinlungah hian a cheng si a. Chu Thlarau Thianghlim hai tute chuan a ruka an do avangin, ‘Pathian thu hi Thlarau Thianghlim chu a ni, Thlarau Thianghlim hran beisei suh u,’ tiin an puang tan mek a ni. Chung mite chuan Pathian ngaihsak anna nei mahse a thiltih theihna (Thlarau Thianghlim leh a hnathawh) an awih lovang. Chutiang mite chuan kan buante, tisa leh thisen ni lo, lalna leh thuneihnate leh he thim chunga khawvel roreltute leh van hmunah te thlarau sualho awmte anih zawk pawh hi ‘thu’ bakin an hre phak lo. Chu Thlarau Thianghlim chu kan Lalpa chuanthli (wind) angin a tehkhin a, chu ngei chu Thlarauva piangte dinhmun sawifiah nan a hmang a ni (John. 3 : 6-8); (Ephesi 6 : 12). Chu thli anga hnathawk thin Thlarau Thianghlim chu nunna a nih miau avangin (Ezekiel. 37 : 9-10).
Saraii ching miau mai hian danglamna awm miah lo va Pathianin a Fapa Krista Kros a lei mihring zawng zawng a tihtawp hmiahna chu chiang takin a rawn tarlang tan a ni. Mihring lama chhuak reng reng hi Pathian nunna kawngah chuan cheibawl leh chhawmtel a tum tawh miau loh avangin. Isua hi Pathian fapa a nih i ring maw, ramhuaite pawhin an ring asin. Khawvel Chhandamtu a nih i ring maw, zu ngawl veil eh nawhchizuar te pawhin an ring asin. ‘Pathianin heng ni tawpah hian a Fapain thu a sawi ta tih i pawm maw, Zofate zawng zawng hian chu thu chu kan pawm awm e. Engnge ni danglamna (difference) lo awm ta? Thlarau Thianghlim hi a ni. Lalpa Isua Krista hming tlangaupuitu mi tam tak hian chu Thlarau Thianghlim hming chu zu dodal tlat a. Chu Thlarau Thianghlim dodalna ngei chu khawtlang kohhran rawihna chhan khu a ni a, chu ngei bawk chu kan rama pawl (Denominational church) sawmruk chuang lo pian chhuah chhan hi a ni. Hriatna mai chuan mihring a tichapo thin a, tisa pawl intaina leh inlak hranna a thlen thin. Pathian Thlarau Thianghlim ngeia mi a pian erawh chuan nun hi a tlawm lo thei lo ni. Inngaitlawm nun a nih avangin inngaihtlawm tum reng pawh a ni lo, a nun chu tlawmsa nun a ni zawk a. Hlauh reng pawh a nei lo zawk hial si a ni. He a hnuaia hla hi tawngtaina hla mawi ber a tling a ni :-				
