He hla chang hnih lek hi thinlung takin i sa thei tawh ngai reng em? Thlarau Thianghlim nei lo     reng reng chun ‘Thlarau’ han tih phat atang hian an meng tal tawp nghal mai thin a ni.
		Hun lokal zelah chuan Abrama chuan ama suangtuah dana fa a nei lo tlat mai chu hrilhhai takin a tawng chhuak ta nghe nghe a, hetiangin, “Aw Lalpa Pathian, eng nge mi pek ang, fa nei lovin ka awm hlen dawn a, ka rokhawmtu tur chu Damaska khua a mi Eliezera hi a ni si a?.... Ngai teh chi reng reng mi thlahtir si lo va” (Gen. 15 : 2,3) tiin. Nimahsela Pathian chuan Abrama chu pawnah a hruai chhuak a, ‘Van lam khi en la, arsite khi i chhiar theih chuan chhiar teh khai.... I thlahte chu khi ti zat khi an la ni ang’ (Gen. 15 : 5) tiin a thutiam chu a thlirtir tawp mai a ni. Hetiang tak hian za-ah za i sawi dik nia i hriat lai siin i tawp ru tlat tawh ngai em? Lalpa hre em ema inngai a, Pathian thu tanchhan atana la chhuak nghauh nghauh a, Thlarau Thianghlim mamawh tih inhriatna reng nei lova mahni felna bawk tihngheh tumtu ka hmuh chang hian helai thu hi a pawimawhzia ka hre chhuak thin.
	Chutiang taka Pathian thil tiam, a tiamna thu chiang bawk si, nimahsela a tihhlawhtlinna kawng mihring lama awm reng reng lo si chu sawiin Zawlnei Isaia lehkhabuah chuan Lal Hezekia manganna thu “Vawiin ni hi manganna leh hmuhsitna ni a ni: naute chu an pian a hun tawh si a, anmahni hring turin chakna awm tawh si lo,” (Isaia 37 : 3) tiin Zawlnei Isaia hnenah thlen a nih kha. Naute piang tur chu Thlarau fa a ni a, anmahni hring turin chakna a awm tawh si lo a ni. Kan ramah pawh hian Thlarau fa nil ova, hriatna fa kan piantir teuh teuh mai hi manganna leh hmuhsitna tipunluntu lek a ni si a. Chu bawk chu Abrama nuna harsatna pawh hi a ni lo bik lo. A thlah lo piang tur chu thutiam fa, mihring lam (an nupa) tawp fel der hnua lo lang tur chu a ni. Pathian thu reng reng hian mihring hi zuk tlawm that a, phuhruk a tum ngai lo va. Mihring chu mi thiat veka mi ei ral a tum zawk a ni. Pathian thuin a ei ral inphal la i tawp fel hma mai ang; i tawp fel veleh thutiam fa nihna chu nangmah ngeiah a lo thleng nghal bawk ang.
	Hun lo kal zelah chuan Saraii mangang chuan ngaihtuah chhuah, ama remruat dana fel thlap bawk si (concrete plan) a rawn phuh chhuak ta hlawl mai le. Saraii chuan a pasal Abrama hnena, “Ngai teh khai, Lalpan fa min neihtir phal loh hi, khawngaih takin ka bawih nu pawl rawh; ama lakah chuan fate ka nei mahna.” (Gen. 16:2) a ti a. Abrama pawhin a nupui remruatna chu a lo pawm ve hmiah a. Hagari (bawihnu) chu a lo pawl ta a; tin a ni chu a rai ta a, a rai tih a inhriat veleh a pi chu a hmusit ta mai a. A va fuh hlel em! A rai lo tur a han rai meuh chuan hmuhsitna a lo chhuak nghal hra mai si a. Tichuan Hagari chuan fapa Ishmaela a hring ta a. Lalpan Ishmaela piang chu a lawm ang em? Roluahtu atan a pawmsak ang maw? Teuh lo mai! ‘Bawih nu chu a fa nen hnawtchhuak rawh, bawihnu fa chuan bawih lo nu fa chu ro a luahpui dawn si lo” tih thu ngaihnobei lo zet chu an remruatna chawh chhuah ve atana Pathian pek chu a ni mauh mai tak a; a ni, kan remruat nen chuan Pathian thiltum chu a va lo inpersan thin em! Pathian Chatuan remruattu hian a committee member atan tumah min lo telh lo hi chu kan ngaihdan chhete tal han rawlh ve zauh te pawh a chakawm thin nen; kan ngaihdan te, kan tum dan te, kan finna leh remhriatnate hi Pathian Chatuan remruatnaah chuan thil lothlawn mai an chang leh thin. Mi fing finna tiboral a, remhre remhriatna a lo paih thlak fel diam tawhna kros hi a mawi ber mai, Chu kros atanga zungkaih (thinlung tihngheh) te chu engtikah mah an nghing dawn si lo va. Tlawmna atanga intan chhuak lo. Thihna kal tlang lo, danglamna lawn liamte hi zawng ruk hmang leh suamhmang mai an la ni reng si a.
	Abrama leh Saraii tan chuan anmahni lam atanga Pathian thil tim tihpuitlin chu thil theih loh hulhual a nihzia a lo lang fiah ta tak tak a. Abrama atanga chi ropui tak chhuak tur chuan fa an neih ngei ngei a ngai si a; tin, chu a fa neih tur pawh chu Pathian pawm ngei (thutiam fa) a nih a tul tlat bawk a ni. Nimahsela mihring nih dan phung pangngai atanga chhui chuan fa han neih chu thil theih ziazang a ni tawh lo. A chhan chu Bible-a kan hmuh angin Saraii chu kum 90 mi niin tar a ni tawh a, chubakah a thla tin thi neih pawh a lo tawp ta bawk a ni. (Gen. 17:17; Gen. 21:5; Heb 11:12). Tin, Saraii chu kum 90 lai a nih tawh avangin, kha leh chen fa nei thei lova lo awm tawh tan khan fa pai leh chu thil awm theia mawi a ni tawh bawk lo. Chuvangin Saraii chin chianzia hi namen lo tak a ni.
	Chutiang taka khawvel lam thlirna atanga thil theih tawh loh hulhual a nih hnu chuan Pathian thutiam chu a lo lang tan ta a. Lalpa ngei chu Abrahama hnenah chuan a rawn inlar leh ta a. Pathian tirh mi pathum inleng a nei ta a. Chung mi pathum te chuan hun a lo thlen tikah Sarin fapa a nei ang tih an rawn hrilh ta a. (Gen. 18:10). Tin, Lalpa chuan a sawi tawh angin Sari chu a zuk kan a, Lalpa Pathian chuan a sawi tawh angin Sari chungah chuan a tihsak bawk a. Tichuan Sari chu a rai a, Pathianin a sawi hun ruat takah chuan Abrahama chu a tar hnuin fapa a hrin sak ta a. (Gen.21:1,2)
	A chunga kan sawi taka tang khian Adama thlah kal zel (Adamic Generation) pangngaia pianna (Genesis of mankind) a tir lama kan sawi tawh mihring pian dan 23 + 23 = 46 chromosomes kha a tawp fel hmiah hnuah, amah Pathian ngei chuan, fapa Isaka, thutiam fa chu a pekin a zuk pe ta a ni. Chuvangin Isaka chu thutiam fa liau liau a ni.
	He dinhmun ang chiah hian mihring Adama thlah zawng zawng hi Abrahama dinhmun ding vek hi kan ni a. Keimahni ringawt hian chatuan nunna (Pathian nena inzawm nun) nei sa kan awm lo va, chatuan thihna nun (Setana nena inzawm nun) chu kan nei zawk a ni. Tin, chu chatuan nunna chu kan thawk chhuakin, kan siam mai thei hek lo. Kan tih dan hrang hrang hian min chhandam phak hek lo. Chutiang taka tawp felte tan Pathianin thutiam fa Isua Krista chu a pekin min rawn pe tawp mai a ni.
	Abrahama hnena thutiam fa Isaka kha pekin awm lo sela, ram tiam peka a awmna kha a tan chuan thihsan atana uihawm tak a ni ringawt mai a ni. Chutiang  chiah bawk chuan fapa peka kan awmna hi a luahna Thlarau Thianghlim tel lo chuan thil uihawm ber a ni ve ringawt mai a ni.
	Abrahama he lei taksa nun kawnga a lo zawh hi kan thlarau nun kawng thu tak inthup chu a ni si a. Hetah hian kan thil chhui lai hi a la tawp hauh lo mai a, a bul tanna ang chauh a la ni. Kan Lalpa Isua Krista kros chuan eng thu ruk nge min lo hnutchhiah i han enfiah zel teh ang. Kros thuchah i man fuh loh chuan Thlarau Thianghlim (Chatuan nunna Krista Thlarau) nei lo hian i nung mai palh hlauh dah ang e. Abrahama ram tiam peka awm chu, Krista peka kan awmna a ni, Isaka (thutiam fa) hlana a awm hnua a thawhlehna ngei chu Abrahama thutiam fa a nihna thu ruk kan tana ram tiam (Krista) luahna Thlarau Thianghlim neihna thu ruk (thu ril) chu a ni.
	Inhlanna thuah kan chhut leh pawhi Abrahama chu thutiam fa tel lo chuan amah ngawta inhlanna chu Pathianin a pawm hauh lo. Pathian khawngaihna avanga inthawina nung leh thianghlim lo awm thei ta hi khawngaihnaah lo chuan inthawina nung anga lang, nung si lo a lo nit lat. Abrahama tana inthawina nung tobul chu, ama inhlanna chu ni lovin, hlan tur nung peka Isaaka zawk chu a ni. Mahni inhlan nun tum reng reng chu hringtu nu tell ova pian tum an ang ber. Hringtu awm lovin tumah an piang ngai hauh si lo va.
	Tichuan, Pathianin Abrahama hnenah, “Abraham,” a ti a; tin, ani chuan “Heta hi ka awm” a ti a. Pathian chuan, “I fapa, i fapa neih chhun, i hmangaih tak, Isaaka ngei kha, hruai la, Moria ramah chuan kal la, chutah chuan ka hrilh tur che tlang pakhatah chuan halral thil hlanah hlan rawh” (Gen. 22: 1-2) a ti a. Abrahama chu a fapa Isaaka hlan tur chuan a insiam a, Pathianin a hrilh na hmun lamah chuan an kal ta a. A chhiahhlawh tlangval pahnih a hruai a, a fapa Isaaka nen. Tin, nit hum niah chuan Abrahama chu a han dak a, a hmun chu hla takah a han hmu ta a. Inthawina hmun tur a hmuh phakna hmunah chuan a chhiahhlawhte chu a dintir a, a fapa nen chauh an kal ta zel a. Abrahama chuan halral thilhlanna tling chu a la a, a fapa Isaaka chu a puttir a, ani chuan mei leh chemte a keng a. Isaaka chuan kalkawnga an kal lai chuan, “Ka pa en teh mei leh thing chu a awm a ; nimahsela halral thilhlan tur beramno chu khawiah nge a awm?” a ti a. Abrahama chuan, “Ka fapa, Pathianin ama tana halral thilhlan tur beramno chu a ngaihtuah chawp mai ang che,” a ti a. Tin, Pathianin a hrilh hmun chu an va thleng a, tin, Abrahama’n chutah chuan maicham a siam a, thing chu a chhep khawm a, a fapa Isaaka chu a phuar a, maicham thing chungah chuan a muttir a. Tin, a kutin a ban a, a fapa tihhlum nan chemte a la a. Tin, Pathian vantirhkoh chuan van atangin amah chu a zuk au va, “Abraham, Abraham,” a zuk ti a. Tin, ani chuan, “Heta hi ka awm,” a ti a. Tin, vantirhkoh chuan, “Naupang chungah khan i kut thlak suh la, amah kha engmah tih hek suh ; i fapa i neih chhun tak pawh mi pek i ui loh avangin Pathian i \ih tih tunah ka hre ta a ni,” a ti a. Tin, Abrahama chu a han dak a, a en a, tin, ngai teh, a hnung lamah chuan berampa a ki thing hnawka lo tang tlat a awm a ; Abrahama chuan berampa chu a man a, a fapa Isaaka aiah halral thilhlanah chuan a hlan ta zawk a. 
	Helai kros thuchah, nunna chabi, Pathian thinlung herhhawnna hi rilru a tawngtai chungin chhiar teh le. Abrahama tan Isaaka chu pek a ni a, chu a fapa pek tak mai chu hlan turin Pathianin a fiah a ni.	
	Abrahama’n a fapa hlanna tur maicham a han siam zawh a, halralna tur thing chhep fela a fapa a han phuar beh thlaphnu a, maicham thing chunga a han zalha, a vih hlumna tur chem a lak khan a thinlung chhungah Isaaka kha a hlan fel der tawh a ni. Hlan turin a kal a, thu a titlu thlap tawh a, a thu tihtluk thlap tawh hnua a chemte meuh a han phawi kha chuan a fapa chu a chiu hlum der tawh a ni. Chutiang taka thinlung entu Pathian chuan, a hlan fel der tawh tih a hriatin, a aiah berampa a rawn pe ta a, chu berampa chu man a, a hlan fel veleh Isaaka chu nungin a lo tho leh ta a ni, Abrahama thinlungah chuan Isaaka chu thi hnu tho leh a ni chiah. Chu ngei chu hriain bible pawhin “Abrahaman Isaaka a hlan” a ti hmiah mai a ni. (Heb. 11:17).
