hat tur thiltih le inzirtirna zawng zawng hi a hut mai a lo nihzia te a lo lang uar uar a. A taka van lam thil chu khawvelah a awm lova, chung van lam thil chu kan hriat phak lohzia hria a, Lalpa ngei pawh tekhin thu-a au a lo ni tih pawh a thlarau chuan min hmuhtir fai vek a ni. Chu veleh chuan awm tan nil leh tawp chin nei tur, chatuan tling lo zawng zawng chu thlan thimah min lum luhpui ta a. Chu hlan thim ngei mai chu pelin, mitthi zing ata thawhlehna ram chu thlarauvin kan lo thleng ta, Lal Isua Krista ram ngei chu (Ph. 3:11). Chu a ram chu he khawvel mi hi a lo ni lo ngei tih kan chiang ta (Joh. 18:36). Kan zan mumang tawpin Krista ta ni thar Thlarau Thiaghlim chuan min hruai hleng ta. A taksa khenbeha lo awm chuan Eden huan, khawvel tantirh ata khawvel tawp nia tihboral tur chu min kawhhmuha, leia a inlarna chuan kan lei taksa leh hringnun chu labovin, chatuanah Krista chu kan thleng  ta, chu ngei chu Pathian remruat awm tan ni nei tawpna chu a ni. Tuna Thlarauva kan luah ta hi Thawhlehna Ram, awmtan ni nei, lak bova lo awm tawhte, mi thianghlimte ruathla nen kan lenna Zion tlang ngei chu a ni si. Kan Lalpa hihna hneh zova tho leh angin thihna khawvel leh hringnun pelin mitthi zing ata chu kan tho ta. A hlimthla i awihna ram khawvel chu lo thim ve thuai se ni tak Kristaah kan lengza ang, keini zawng kan khawsakna van a ni si a. keini zawng lei hringnun hi pelin mi thianghlim ne tualkhat kan lengza a, lei dana zir chi a ni ta lo.
          Lei lama zung kaia van lama kan thiang thin kha, lei lama kan zung zawng zawng pawt chhuakin van lamah min phun ta daih a, tunah hian lei, Aigupta-ah kan inlar a ni tih kan puang e. Chu ngei chu  kan Lalpa remruatna dinhmun dik tak chu a lo ni si (Eph. 2:5-7; Heb. 12:22-24; Ep. 2:19;m 2Kor. 12:1-6; Joh. 17:6).
         Tichuan he lei hnuk leh marphu a chawlh hma si hian mitthi tho leh ramah thlarauvin kan pem ta daih a ni. Lei dan a zir chi hauh lo tirhkohvin a lo sawi kha, “A thihna anpuia thiin amah nen, a thawhlehna nen ka hriat theih nan, mitthi zing ata thawhlehna chu ka chang the ihram mahna, “(Ph. 3:10) tia a sawi angin, chu thihna hmun tak tak chu meiling rah anga chiang a han tuar  chuan, “Krista hnenah khenbehin ka awm ta;nimahsela, ka nung a ni; keimah erawhchu ka ni tawh lo, Krista chu keimahah a nung zawk a ni, “(Gal. 2:20) tia a sawi kha, a mihring hlui khenbehna Rom. 6:6-a a sawi kha ni tawh lovin, mihring thar, Suala ni lo Pual ngei mai khenbeha chu a sawi zawk a ni. Gal. 14:17-ah phei chuan, “Kei erawh chuan kan Lalpa Isua Krista Kros lo chu ka chhuan loh tur zia mai chu chu mi azarah chuan khawvel hi ka tan khenbehin a awm ta, keipawh khawvel tan khenbehin ka awm a ni..... Tun achinah chuan tumahin mi tibuai tawh suh se, ka taksaah hian Isua chinchhiahnate ka pu si a,” tiin a sawi ta a ni. Thurin (Doctrine) avanga danglam mai ni tawh lovin, Puala a danglam ta bawih a ni.
            Zofate hian Pathian thu hi kan pawnhpaw awih lutuk a, a nih theih leh theih loh ngaihtuahna tak tak nei lo hian kan Amen thlup thlup zel a. Thil ni thei ngei a nih leh nih loh lam kan chhut ngai lo. He Jakoba Pathian, mahni ngeia Krista thuruk Thlarau Thianghlimin a rawn thlen tir hi i la tawng lo a nih ngat chuan Pathian thu ka ring i tih hi rin bar i lo nei lo tih inhmu chhuak ang che. Rinna kawnga kal emaw i intih lai khan hriat tur kawng lek i la zawh tih hi awi phal ang che. Hmuh theiha kalte’n Thlarau Thianghlim zara lo awm chu an hre phak lo. 
              Jakoba nun kawng hi mi tam takte piantharna thusawi nan kan hmang thin a. Chu chu ni hauh lovin, “Nangin Israela thlahte hnenah chuan, Lalpa Pathian chuan in hnenah mi rawn tir a ni e: Hei hi kumkhuaa ka hming chu a ni a, tin, hei hi chhuan zawng zawng thlenga mi hriat rengna chu a ni,’ ti ang che,” (Ex. 3:15) titu chuan awmze nei takin ‘Jakoba hi min lo pe a ni. Jakoba chu a mizia leh nunphung kan enin pa rem hria leh pa fing, hmagchang hre tak mai leh chimlim tak a ni a. Pathianin a fa Isaaka hmanga a lo chhan chhuah tawh malsawmna chuan mihring thar pawhin Krista malsawmsakna kan awmna rah chu seng tumin rem hre tak leh mangchang hre takin engkim a ruahman thin. Beiseina sang tak neiin Pathian duhzawng hriatna leh a lo khawl khawm tawhte hmangin a bei a ni. Nimahsela Pathian chuan a khawl khawm loh hmang enkawl chu a kohna a ni si a.
           Jakoba chuan chu finna hmang chuan a thawk a, a thawh rah chu a seng ngei mai, ama ngaih chuan. Mahse a kotu Pathian thihna, “ I thlarau ramah leh i laichinte hnenah haw leh tawh rawh, I hnenah ka awm zel dawn nia,” (Gen.31:3) tia a hrilh angin Jakoba chu a puzawn Labana hnen atangin a hawng leh tan ta a. Nimahsela kalkawnga a kal laiin a u Esauva hnen ah zualko a tir a, chung a mi tirhte chuan, “I u Esauva hnen kan va thleng a, tin, mi zali rual rawn hruaiin hmuak tur chein a lo kal nghe nghe a sin,” (Gen. 32:6) tiin an sawi a. Chutia an han hrilh veleh chuan Jakoba chuan a hlau em em a, a mangang ta a, a u Esauva tlawn lungawi nan a ranrual tam tak te chu pawl hniha siamin a hmaah a kaltir ta a. Rim taka a lo thawhchhuahsa chu a u a lo bum tawh tlawn lungawi nan chuan a pe ral ta teuh mai. Hei hian kan mihring thar Pathian hriatnaa rawng kan bawlte hi thil lohthlawnah a ral a, hriatna nasa tak hmanga kan tih pianthar chum ehumte hi min tibeidawngtu lek an chang thie thin. Thlarau Thianghlim hrinte chauhvin Krista chu nun nan an h, ang si a.
          Tichuan Jakoba chu mangang em ema awmin Pathian hmaah chuan a kaikun a, “Aw ka pu Abrahama Pathian, ka pa Isaaka Pathian, aw Lalpa ‘I ram lamah leh i laichinte hnenah haw leh tawh rawh, tichuan kan tit ha ang ce, mi titu, i chhiahhlawh chunga khawngaihna zawng zawng i lantir leh thu tak ka ni lo ve; he Jordan lui hi tiang nen chauh ka kan a, tunah zawng pawl hnih zet ka lo nih tak hi. Khawngaih takin ka u kut ata, Esauva kut ata ngei chu, mi chhanhim ang che; nunna chawpa min rawn thah vek ka hlau si a. Nangin, ‘Ka tithe ngei ngei ang chia, i thlahte tuifinriat tiau vaivut chhiar sen loh hial khawpa tam angin ka siam ang e,’ i ti a,” a ti a (Gen. 32:9-12). Jakoba tawngtaina hi a va mawi tak em! Pathianin amah a khawngaihna leh thu tak a lo lantir tawh zawng zawng zinga a te nau ber pawh phu lo hliah hliahin a inhmu leh ta a ni. Hriattirna ropui tak kan tlangaupui te, Pathian thutiam ropui tak tak sawi dum dum tute hi Thlarau Thianghlim hnar tlattute kan ni tih hre turin han thangharh hlawm teh ila aw! Pathian hian a fapa leia a rawn tirh hnu hian a fapa Krista Isua bak chu mihring a hmang ngai lo tih hre lova, Pathian mi hman nia inngaite hin malpui ruhtuah pelh hun an han tawk ve tur chu Zoram hian a nghakhlel thin teh e.Mihring tawngka hian a sawi fiah zo lo va, Thlarau Thianghlim chauh ti a kan zavaia ka kan an hun hunah chu Zion tlang Thlarau lama mitthi zing ata thawhlehna chu lei kohhran ngei hian a la rap ang. Chu ngei chu Thuthlung Thar chhut a ni a, chu ngei bawk chu Zoram nghahfak, Hmangaihna hrui vuana thinlung hmun khat pua kan hnamin kal a siam tak takna tur chu a ni. Chu chhuatah chuan pawl (Denomination) reng a awm si lo va.
               Jakoba chuan a tawngtaina hmun ngeiah chuah riah hmun a rem ta rap mai a. Chuta tang chuan azan azanin a tho va, a nupuite pahnih leh a bawih nute pahnih leh a fa sawm leh pakhat te chu hruaiin Iobbok lui kaiah chuan a kai ta a. Tichuan anni chu a hruai a, lui chu a kaitir a, a neih zawng zawng pawh a kaitir bawk a. He Jabbok lui kai hi i thleng tawh reng em? I nupui fanau zawng zawng te, i thil neih zawng zawng te kha he Jabbok lui kaiah hian i kaipui taw hem? Tuna in chhungkaw ei leh in, silh leh fen, in chhung bungbel leh bungraw dang reng rengte ngun takin bih la, Lalpa hmaah in chungkaw taksa leh rilru leh thlarau dinhmun in kalpui danah khan Lalpa rilru tihnatna kawng a awm chhung chuan hmangaihtu vuakna che a tawp lo vang tih hi hria ang che. Krista ni chu a hnai tawh si a! (Thes. 3:13; 5:23; 1Kor. 1:8; Phi. 1:6-11) A hmangaihte chu an malpui ruh chuktuah a pelh hma chuan a vaw mai a ni. 
              Tichuan Jakoba chu amah chauhvin a awm ta a. He Jakoba Pathian a nihna anga Lalpa inlarna thuruk chang tur hian mi dang ngaihdan te, mi thiamte sawi dan te, hrilhfiahtute ziak reng reng hi thlir lova, mahni chauh tak taka Lalpa pawlna hmun (Daniela pindan)-ah a inlar a ni. Chu hmunah chuan cham reg a, mipui kal liam nghak a. Lalpa remtih hunah a ruang lak thlak thlan hawn thleng en tura rawn kan ni a. Jerusalem dai, he khawvel hringnun chhuah phak a ni lo ve. A ni, mi dangin an hril theih loh, thihna hneha tho leh Krista ngei mai a taka inlarin a ni avangin, darthlalanga inhmuh riai ruaina ram a ni tawh lo va, Lalpa chu hmaihma ngeia thlarauva tawhna ram a ni.
               PENIEL: Jakoba amah chauhva a awm chu mi pakhatin khawfingehah thlengin a buan a buan a. Tin, a hneh lo tih a inhriatin Jakoba malpui ruh chuktuahah chuan a khawihsak, tichuan a buai lai chuan Jakoba a malpui ruh chuktuah chu a pelhsawlh ta a. Tin, ani chuan, “Mi thlah rawh, khawfing pawha chah dawn tawh hi,” a ti a. Tin, Jakoba chuan, “Mal mi sawm loh chuan ka thlah lovang che,” a ti a. Tin, ani chuan, “I hming chu Jakoba an ti tawh lo vang a, Isreala an ti zawk taw hang; Pathian leh mihring i bei a, i hneh tawh si a’” (Gen. 32:24-28) a ti a. “Tin, chutah chuan mal a sawmsak ta a. Tin, Jakoba chuan chu mi hmuh hmingah chuan PENIEL a vuah ta a: Pathian chu a hmaihma ngeiah ka hmu a, ka nunna hi a zuah a ni si a,” a ti a. Tin, Peniel a pelh lai chuan ni a lo chhuak a, amah chu a rawn chhun a, a malpui avang chuan a lo bait a a. Chuvangin tun thlenngin Isreala thlahte chuan malpui ruh chuktuahah khel tha awm hi an ei ngai lo: Jakoba malpui ruh chuktuah chu a khel tha lai taka a khawih avangin,” (Gen. 32:29-32).
                He a chunga kan chhiar takah khian Jakoba malpui ruh chuktuah pelhsawlh ta chug entail Israel te chanvo a ni a, a khel tha tak khi hnam Israel-te chanvo ‘thuruk’ a nit hung (Rom. 11:25-26).
                Jakoba malpui ruh chuktuah a lo pelhsawlh veleh khan enge ni lo thleng ta: Pathian leh mihring a lo buan hneh ta a ni. Chu mihring a buan hneh tak chu tunge ni keini tan kan tih chuan mihring thar, hriatna lama hausa em em leh sang tak mai chu a ni a, khawih pelhsawlh chu tunge kan tih chuan, Thlarau Thianghlim ngei chu a ni. Chu Pathian Thlarau Thianghlim chuan Kros thiltihtheihna bawk hmangin mihring thar chu a chakna lai ber, a malpui ruh chuktuah a khawih pelh (namthu) ta rup mai a.
                Thlarau Thianghlim hmanraw ropui, ringtu zawng zawng tana Krista awm reng theihna KROS tel lo chuan hriat tur leh thiamna, sawi rinna leh mihring thahnemngaihna leh remruatna zawng zawng chu, a langah ropui hle thin mahse Kros lo chuan chung zawng zawng chu Laipui mu awm lo kah ang lek fang a lo ni tih hmuhchuakin Lalpa hmaihmaah mihring thar ngei mai chu a lo tuiral leh ta a ni.
               Chu mihring thar chuan a Lalpa a lo belhbul tum dan zawng zawng chu mahin (ama) lawmna zawng mai thin a lo nihna te, thlarau lainatna nei lova tawngtai mai mai thin a lo nihna te, a tobul ngei kalsan avanga ro ngawih ngawih leh lawm theih hauh loh a nihte chu hrechuakin, hmngaihna hmasa bansantu chuan a Lalpa Kros chauh chu chhuangin Kros chu a belbul leh ta a; a ni, chu Kros ngeiah chuan zung kaihin thlan atanga thawhlehnaah chuan kan tiak chhuak a ni si a, Vawiin an zungkaihna Kros kalsana hrin an han tum thin hi chu, thing a zung chawpa kar phawh tawh hi tui leiha vawm hrih reng tum ila hlawhtlin a awl zawk phian awm e! Hmangaihtu thla zar hnuaiah van nun kan chen thin a ni si a.
                 Pathian buan hnehna ve thung chu enge ni ang le? He Jakoba nuna Pathian buan hneh hi a ropuiin a ril hle mai. Ani Jakoba Pathian hriatna ngei chu a ni si a. A hgretu mihring thar leh a hriatna ngei chu a ral leh ta. (IIKor. 5:16-17). A hretu leh hriatna ngei mai hman tlak loh a nihzia han hmuh chuan boruakn lang ang maiin thih hian tawpintai awm lovin, ral hian kin ni reng a nei lova, ni tin thiin amahah amah nilo Krista chu a lo nung reng zawk a, chu nitin thihna pawh chu thihsual nun nil ova, sualte a thihna zawk nun, Kalvari Kros-in (Tlamgmawi ber maiin) mi fela a puan chhuah tawhte khai kana kan awmna zawk chu a ni. Chu thihna nun kawng zawhtute kalkawng chu a zim em em a, a kalte thung chu an zau em em thung si a ni. Nimahsela zau em em e ti lo chuan sual si per hlek pawhin lianpuiin a kam thin a, a kang nghal zel thung tlat si. Chung mite chu Krista neitu an in lova, Kristan a neih zawk an ni. Thlarau Thianghlim changtu an nil ova. Thlarau Thianghlim chan an ni, Isua Krista ka tan an ti tawh lova, Isua Krista tana khaithawh an ni. Chu dinhmun danglam tak chu an chenna a nih vangin nuam an zawng lova, hrehawmin a tuar zawk a, chawimawina leh fakna an tan a kha a, tihduhdahna leh sawichhiatna a thlum thung a, ropuina leh Lalna chu Krista tan an kian fel hmiah a. T lawmna leh thuhnuairawlhna chuan an thinlung Lalthut thleng chu a vawng nung tlat reng a ni. Chhuah nil eh tlak ni awm lo Ropui Lalpa a tak mi chu a eng renf a, chu eng chuan an taksa thi thei ngei an taksa thi thei ngei hnuk leh marphu chawlh hnua, an thlan thlengin a en kulh mai tih hmuh theih loh Pathian lunglohtui chu Kalvari fenthlir ngeia dawhin, chu lunglohtui luanna sira Hawilopar, he lei hringnun rama par chhuak ngai reng reng lo chu a tawn veleh chu lunglohtui chu a han in a, chuveleh chuan khawvel a ngaihna zawng zawng chu a lo ral ta vek a. Khawvel a ngaihna zawng zawng a lo chuai hnu chuan pialral lam panin hlim takin hmangaihtu chenna ‘Paradise’ kan Jerusalem-ah huan thlarauvah Pathiang chhungte nen tualkhata leng zain, van chhungkua, hmuh theih loh kohhran, Lalpan a Mo thianghlim a buatsaih, a en nin theih ngai reng reng lohna chuan a pem ta a ni.
                 Chu hmun chu Hringlangtlang dingte chuan an hmu phak ngai reng reng lova, a rim erawhchu an tem ve zuah zuah thin. Chu hmun thleng tawhte tan chuan he lai ropuina zawng zawng pawh hi nunna thlarau atan chuan tui farkhatah khawvel leh lei hringnun boral leh tur a din chhuah hma a, Pathian Chatuan khawpui mawi tak chu ringtuten he lei hringnun taksa an put lai ngeia an luah theih Lalpa nena chen dunna hmun thawhlehna Ram ngei chu thlarauah kan lo thleng ta.
                  Jakoba chu bumtua ni tawh lova, Pathian lalfa tia vuah tak a lo ni ta a. Tirhkoh Puala te, Joba te, David ate, thurin (Doctrine) avanga danglam satliah mai ni tawh lova, anmahni ngei an lo ganglam ta ang khan Israela, Jakoba thar tak tak chu hai rual a ni ta lo. Amah atang ngei chuan Pathian hnam thlan Abrahana a koh nia a lo tiam tawh Israel hnam sawm leh ham hnih cu an lo chhuak tar eng a ni. Chu chu a kohhran thianghlim thu ruk chu a ni e.
                  He Jakoba Pathianah hian Zoram ringtute kan luh hun chuan Pawl tin pindanna bang hi tihchima awmin pakhatah (pawl khatah ni lo) kan luang thei taw hang a. Israel-ah Israel hnam 12 an lo chhuak angin, Pawl (Denomination) anga kan rawngbawlna ata hnam (Mizo Zoram) kan nihna angin khawvel hnam tin chi tin hnenah Krista lokal lehna (Ram Chanchin Tha) chu hrilhin hnam thlarau thihsanin (Tlawmngaihna dik tak hnam dangten an neih ve miah lo chu) hnam tinrengte unau kan nihna rilru (Kros Thuchah) puin kan Lalpa thuchah tluantling chu a famkim in kan hril ang a, chu ngei chuan Krista mo (kohhran thianghlim chu a siam puitling tawh ngei ang. Thlarau Thianghlim Pathian fa tak takten hmuh theih pawlah hmuh theih loh kohhran rawng chu bawl ngam turin tunah hian kan hnam Lalpan min au ta a ni. Pawla awmte erawh chuan a tluantlingin an puang thei lovang.
              Jakoba chu Peniel atangin Sekem-ah, Sekem atangin Bethel-ah, Bethel atangin Hebron-ah a kai zel a. Chu Hebron hmuh ngei atang chuan Pathian aw thar a lo thleng ta a. Josefa awmna Aigupta-ah Pathianin thian anga a lo thleng ta a. Aigupta ramah ngei chuan khawvel lal Pharoa chu mal a sawmsak ta a ni (Gen. 46: 2-4; Gen. 47:7). Chu ngei chu tho leh fate khawvel (Aigupta)-a inlar lehna dan mawi tawp khawk chu a ni e. Chu chu chhuak-lut te chanvo a ni.
              Jakoba Pathian a nihna anga Pathian mihringtea a nipuanna: Thawhlehna Ram hi he hmuh theih khawvel piah ram, hringnun rengin a chim phak loh Mi thiamnghlim kal leh hmaa thlarauva rawn inhre chhuak a ni. Chu hmun chu hmuh theih taksa hmun kan luah ang bawka tlarauva luah nghal theih, thlarau hmun a nih avangin Thlarau Thianghlim hruaia awm mekte zawng zawng tan he Thawhlehna Ram chanchin hi a hlu a ni. Ram hmasa thuruk a nih avangin taksa khawvel hausakna leh ram luahna anga ngaia duh luat vanga lo au sual tawhte pawh an awm a, chung mite chu an demawm lo, a vei lam hi lak tel ve awl tak reng a ni a; Ram thuthlung leh hnam thuthlung leh Lal thuthlung kalpui mekte pawhin he thlarauva kan luah ram ngei hi hmuh theih khawvel ropuina emaw an tih vang chauh a ni. Nimahsela, kan Lalpa ngeiin, “Ka ram chu he khawvel ami hi a ni lo,” tia a lo sawi taw hang khan, chu ram luahna thuthlung zawng zawng chu thlarauva luah chi a lo ni a. Chu thlarauva Tlang thianghlim luahtute chuan Krista lokal lehna leh kum 1000 Lalram chanchin leh chatuan vanram (Ram Chanchin Tha) an hril zawh hnuin boruakah Lalpa hmuak turin an chho tawh dawn a ni. Chu ngei chu mi thianghlim lawr (Taksa thawhlehna hmasa) chu a ni a. Khawvel Indopui III-na lo thlen hma chiahin chu taksa tlanna, rah hmasate chanvo chua lo thleng ang. Khawvel tihboralna hmasa, tuilet (Flood) lo thlen hma chiah a, mithianghlim Thianghlim) rah Hmasate Harmageddon lo thlen hma chiah lawr an nihna tur chu a lo entir a. Chu mi thianghlim lawr turte tihdanglam an nih dan tur chu Elija (Translated Saint) vana lak chhohva awm khan a lo entir a, chutiang bawkin tihdanglam (Translated) an ni ang. Tin, mi thianghlim muhil tawhten chu taksa thawhlehna hmasa change Krista lokal leh ruala an chan tur chu Mosia (Resurrected Saint) Israelte hruaitu chuan a lo entir a ni. (2Lalte 2:11; Gen. 5:24; Dent. 34:5-6).
              Mi thianghlim kal hmasaten Thlarauva thawhlehna an chan dan:-
              Rinnaa fak lo hlawh tawh mi thianghlim kal hmasate pawh khan he tuna kan saw Thawhlehna Ram hi chu vawi-leh-khatah an luah mai bik lova. Eng vang nge kan tih chuan, “Keini tel lo va tihfamkima an awm loh nan,” (Heb.11:40) tia ziak ang hian Pathian engkim siamtu leh remruattu chuan, a chatuan remruat leh thil tum tihhlawhtlinna tak tak chu a fapa Isua Krista lo lanna ni hmasa atan a lo khek hriau hriau reng a. Chutiang  taka Pathian remruatna fing tak chu a hun tak zelah a rawn inkeu ta. Krista thihna leh thawhlehna vang liau liauvin mi thianghlim kal tawhte thlarau chuan an thlan mitthi khua chu chhuahsanin Lalpa Isua thawhleh rualin rualin an lo tho va, khaw thianghlim kan Jerusalem (Paradise) ah an inlar (pem) ta siau siu a ni (Mt. 27:52,53).
            Keini tan:- Ringtute hian kan nunna (The life of our life) Kirista Thlarau Thianghlim hruaina zelin kan Lalpa leh chhandamtu hniakhnung (Foot print of our Lord) kan lo zawh chho zel a lo ni a. Chu Thlarau Thianghlim  chu min a neih loh chuan a tir ata a ngai reng a la ni. (2Kor. 3:6) Hriatna kawngah hmasawn hle mahse nun Krista chu a hmang thei chuang lo. Chu Pathian Thlarau Thianghlim hruaia awmte chu Pathian fate an nih avangin Krista nun kawng  chu a takin he leia an taksa awm lai ngei hian chu an lut a, chu nun thuruk mawi tak  mai an thlen chuan anmahni chu an thianghlim famkim ta tihna ni lovin, thianghlimna kawng chu an kawng zawh a nih miau avangin chu nun kawng thianghlimna chuan ni tin an nun ngei chu a tifai chho ta tak a ni. Chung mite chuan he lei bawlhhlawhna hi chu an chhuahsan tak tak a, khawvel hmun nihna atang hi chuan an thianghlim ta ngei a, thianghlimnain khawvel hi an ep ngam a ni (Is. 35:1-10; 2Kor.12:1-6; Kol. 3:10).
             Chu famkimna chuan taksa, rilru leh thlarau (Mihring bawlhhlawhna ramri chu pelin an zawh chu thianghlimna kaawng ni ngei mahsela, an Lalpa Thianghlimna engah chuan an bawlhhlawzia chu an inhmu reng tho ani. He famkimna nun hi Jentailte ni kin (Lk. 21:24) it e, Jentailte famkimna tih te (Rom 11:25) Mitthi zing ata thawhlehna (Ph. 3:11) tih te, Zion tlang, van Jerusalem, Pathian nung khua (Heb. 12:22) tih te, van (Ph. 3:20) tih te, leh Pathian chhungkua (Ep. 2:19) ti tein tawngkam dang dang chu thlarau chawlhna hmun sawi fiah nan Bible  chuan a hmang a. Chu thawhlehna chu thu chah mai ni lova, hunin a rawn her chhuahpui a nih avangin kan Lalpa lokal lehna pawhin chu thuchah luahna chu puan zawh a nih chuan a rawn zui nghal dawn a ni ( 1Kor. 15:20-24). Chu mitthi zing ata thawhlehna chu thlarauva kan thlen veleh mi thianghlimte nen tual khata lengzain, tawngkam (thu) maia kan lo  hril thin kha Thlarau Thianghlim thlarauvah min hruai thleng ta a ni. Chu tlang atang ngei chuan Thlarau Thianghlim chuan inralrinna thu a rawn puang ta. Zion atanga inralrinna thupuan ngei chu (Joela 2:1-11). Lalpa ni ropui leh hmingthang rapthlak tak bawk si chu a lo thlen dawn avangin (Jer. 30:7; Jer. 46:21; Is. 63:4; Daniela 12:1; Joela 2:31; Mt. 24:21; Thup. 6:17) INRALRIN A HUN TA E!
              Khawvel mi thiamte chuan nasa taka an zir hunah hriat reng an lo neih lohzia an inhmu chhuak thin. Chutiang khawvel mi thiamte thil siam chhuah leh an thu leh hla pawh chu keini a zir ve lo tan chuan awi harsa tak a ni. Pathian thu leh lek phei chu chutiangmi ropuite pawh chuan an ring phak lo a ni. Finfiah leh hmuh chhuah phak rual an ni lova, khawvel thil anga a dikna chawh chhuah theih mai chi lo vek zawk a lo ni lehghal. Thlarau Thianghlim hruaia awmte chuan mihring thluak leh hhia leh tha hriatna khawl tlin loh hiala rill eh thuk chu hriat theihna Pathianin a pe tlat a ni. Chu thuruk thlarau lam nun chu a inpuannate chauh chuan an hria a, mihring mihrinna mi mawl zawk anga langte hnenah paawh a puang miau a ni. Chu thuruk leh ril chang tura thil tul ber pakhat chu Pathian thu(Bible) leh Thlarau Thianghlim hruaina chan kawp a ni. Bible thu ngaisangtute tam takten thinlung lama thawk thin hmuh theih loh Thlarau Thianghlim leh a hnathawh chu an awi loh bur avangin an hriatnaah chuan an tawp bel a. Lehlamah ve thung chuan Thlarau mi inti tam takte chuan a rau lam pang chauh chu an hlut a, Bible thu leh thuchah (Sermon) lam an hlamchhiah thung. Chutiang mi chi hnih kar (a laiah) ringtu nun nhet chu a dang a ni. Samari mi thian Suamhmang tawk enkawl nana duli pahnih Khualbuk vengtu hnena a pek kha, chu thil pahnih Bible (thu) leh Thlarau Thianghlim chu a ni si a. Chutiang tak chuan Bible thuin a lo sawi ngei Thawhlehna nun thianghlim chuThlarau Thianghlim-ah luah theih a ni. Amah Thlarau Thianghlim chu tho leh Krista kai thotu a nih vangin. Chu Thlarau Thianghlim ngei chuan Krista thawhlehna hnathawh thiltihtheihna thawahlehna thiltihtheihna ngei chu mihringte hnena pek a tiam chu a ni (Ph. 3:10). Chu thawhlehna thlarauva kan chan tura ruat chu mahni hun theuh zelah kan chang a, chu hun chu kan Lalpa lokal lehna (2nd coming) hma ngei a nih angin tunah hian kan chang ta (Kor. 15:22-25). Chu Thawhlehna chu Thlarau lam thuruk a nih vangin mi tam tak chuan Krista lokal leh huna taksa thawhlehna tueah an ngai a ni, Thlarau Thianghlim thuruk a nih vangin (1Kor. 2:7-16).                     
          Chutiang tak chu Pathian thu hi a nih avangin, he thawllehna ram, mitthi tawh (Taksa thihna kaltlang tawh) mi thianghlimte nena tual khat kan lenzana hmun ngei pawh chu i awih phak loh ram vek a nih ka ring a; chu i awih hauh loh hmun i rawn thlen hun chuan nangmah leh i lo hriat tawhte chu chhuan tlak reng a awm lo tak meuh tih hriain, Pathian khawngaihna hnathawh, lei leh van Lalberin a fate min lo pek chu a lo thukzia  leh sanzia hriain, i ngaihdan, phung chem lawm taka i lo lawm thinte chu i zep tel ngam bik lo vang. Zeh tel ahnekin, hriat reng i lo neih lohzia zawk chu hmuin, hmuh tur tak hming chung-nung ber chu chatuana ropuina i p eve tlawk tlawk mai ang. Tichuan inngaihtlawm tum ran mi chapo khan chapo luih theih hauh lohna hmun chu i thleng ve ta tih i hre chhuak phut mai ang.
         He leia pawl thlarau changtute leh pawl-lo-pawl thlarau changtute hian chu hmun chu an thleng rih lo. Chu hmun thlengtute zawng chu an nunah eng thlarau dang maha tel tawh lo, chatuan khawvar engah an leng tawh a ni. Kan Lalpa min tirh ang zelin pawl tinah kan inlar a, “Nimahsela, Kristan hnehnaa min hruai fotu leh, keimahni hmanga hmun tina amah hriatna rim hriattirtu Pathian hnenah lawm thu awm rawh se. Chhandam mekahte leh boral mekahte chuan Pathian tan Krista rimtui kan ni si a; pawl khatte tan chuan thihna lakah thihna tur rim kan lo ni a, pawl khatte tan chuan nunna laka nunna tur rim kan lo ni a,” (2Kor. 2:14-16) tih ziak angin kan mumang ram ata zing ni eng mawi ber Krista chu kan nun ngeiah theuh lo chhuak thuai se, khawvel ni eng lei hringnun ram hi pelin Thawhlehna ni eng mawi ber Krista-ah lengza ila, a va hlimawm dawn em!
                          Thawhlehna Lal Isuan Leiah a zirtir:-
