“NANG MUHIL MENG LA,
MITHI ZING ATA THO RAWH,
TICHUAN KRISTA CHUAN 
A CHHUN ENG ANG CHE;” (Eh. 5:14).
            Kan Lalpa chu thova nung leh mai a ni lo va, thawhlehna leh nunna tunah leh chatuan atan a ni si a. Krista Isua-ah chuan ama rual veka min kai thovin, van hmunahte ama hnenah min thuttir ta.” (Ep. 2:6). Kan nunna Krista chu a tho tawh, nunna nen tunge awm hrang ngai le? Kan nunna Krista-ah chuan chatuan atan tihnunin kan lo awm reng si a.
             Thawhlehna ram, kan hmunah a ni Lalpan Thlarau lam malsawmsahna tinreng min sawmna hmun chu. A hmun lova thil dawn tum chu beidawnna a ni thin. Van hmunah erawh chuan Thlarau lam malsawmsak chu a thleng reng a ni. Khel lova malsawmsakna ramah ruathlain cheng la, i lei hringnun pawh a lo danglam vek nghal ang. “Chutichuan, Krista hnenah kaithawhin in awm ve tawh chuan, chung lam, Pathian ding lama thu Krista awmna thil awmte chu zawng rawh u. Chung lama thil awmah te chuan in rilru nghat tlat rawh u, leia thil awmahte chuan nghat lovin. In thi tawh a, in nunna chu Pathianah chuan Krista hnenah thuhrukin a awm si a,” (Kol. 3:1-3). “ Ani chuan kan thil tih angte ni lovin, ama ruat leh khawngaihna ang zawkin min chhandam a, kohna thianghlimin min ko bawk a; chu khawngaihna chu leilung pian hmain (chatuanah) Krista Isua-ah chuan min pek a ni tawh, nimahsela, min chhandamtu Krista Isua inlarna avang hian tunah (TUNAH) tihlanin a awm ta. Ani chuan thihna chu a tiboralin. Chanchin thain nunna leh boral theih lohna a tilang a.” Tiin Timothea hnenah Tirhkoh Paula chuan a thawn a ni (2Timo. 1:9-11). Helai thua Thihna tihborala awm leh boral theih lohna thu hi he lei mihring dam vhhung rei lo te sawi na a ni lova. Kan damchhung tawi te, chum rei lo te lo lang a ral leh mai thin hi sawi tham ;leh enghelh tlak a ni n hek lo. He lei hringnun tawi te leh thereng pakhat pawh siam thei lo mihring finna te hi kalsanin, i Pathian thu kha chatuan rilruin chhiar la, tun hi chatuan thawhlehna hun ropui a nihzia kawngaih i var vet hut mai ang! Chu thu Thawhlehna chuan lei taksa thihna tur zawng zawng pawh a lak bosak chein, khawlvel buaina tui fawn leh tahna thlipui chung lamah rinna thian i leng delh delh tawh mai angg. Chu velah chuan phur rit tla fai vekin Krista nghawngkawl zang tak mai chu i Lalpa Thlarau Thianghlim ngei chuan a bahtir nghal ang che. Tichuan, Unau, puan ropui sina hnenah tumkau vaite zingah it el ve tar eng mai tih i hria ang. Duhten kan awih-za-na tlang thianghlimah lenrual lungduh zawng te lo chho rawh u. Chu tlanga chengte chuan eng pawl mah tai an nei lova, eng pawl rawng mah an bawl bawk lova, tuman an rilru an tina pha bawk lo. Lalpa chu an tan a hlu ngawih ngawih a, an Lalpa chu engkima an engkim a nih avangin an Lalpa rawngbawl chu lungawi take m em a, an Lalpa pawhin a ngaina ngawih ngawih tih an hai bik lo.
               Mi thianghlim rauthla nena kan lenna tual nuam chu alawm Thawhlehna Ram tla min hrilh chu. Mi thianghlim kal ta te pawh kha Krista thihna avangin an thlan a lo inhawng a, a thawhleh rualin an lo tho va, khaw thianghlimah chuaan an leng ta. Chung mite thawhlehna leh nunna chu Krista chu a ni a. Chu thawhlehna leh nunnaah chuan kan lo thanharh velah mi thianghlimte nen a kutphah roui chhungah tualkhat kan leng za a. Keini tell ova tihfamkima awm bik lote nen tunah keini telin tualkhat kan lengza a. Chung lam Jerusalem chu an nu a ni a, chu ngei chu keini nu pawh a nih avangin, chhul khat kual Krista (Eden tharah) kan lengza a ni. A va hlimawm em! Chu ngei chu kan chatuan kawngkhar ropui, kan Jerusalem thar Kros hneh nan min hawnsak, tuman an khar leh theih leh tawh loh chu a ni ngei si a. Ropui Isuan min chhandam ta. A tan thiin kan nung leh ta. Chatuan thihna a la bo ta. Chatuan nunna kan lo chang ta. Kan tan hmun a siam z ova, a hnenah min hruai ta. Van leh khawvel kan pumbil ta e. Lei kan rochung ta. Chu Van hmun leh khawvel kan pumbil ta e. Lei kan rochung ta. Chu Van hmunah ngei chuan kan Lal Krista, hunbi kim khawsak huna lo kal leh tur chu kannnghak a ni. Amahah chuan leia thil awmte vana thil awmte fawk khawm mekin kam awm a, a hunbi a lo kim hunah a chatuan ramah chatuan nunna neitu, chatuan ram, thlarauva luah tawhtuten kan chang vek ang. Chumi ni ropui taka tan chuan ka pasal Krista chuan Krista chuan Thawhlehna tlang chengte chu a rawn phet (Signal) reng tawh a ni.
                  Khawvel mi ropuite chuan an hma lam kum 5000 huna thil lo awm tur an suangtuah pha ve a, mipui mimir chuan kan dam chhung hun bak hi kan suangtuah pha meuh lo. Chu kan suangtuahna pawh chu hma lam darker khata kana wm dan tur pawh hre lovin kan ark haw thim dai a. Chu kan rin thua kan suangtuah chu hrilhin kan zeldin thu bawlah kana r awp zuankai ve ngawt a; chutianga suangtuahna nei tha zawkte thu-hla chu tuipuiin mipate chu Iungkun vhungah kan Zawng rual thut thup mai a nih hi. Pathian chatuan remruattu erawh chuan chatuana ral thei tawh lo, hunbi leh kum tin an sawhsawn rual loh chu a fapain a puang ta. Chatuan khua a var ta. Chatuanah (Krista-ah) kan thangharhin kan zan tawnmang mawl, he lei nun chhung leh hun leh kum hi kan kal pelt a. Lei leh a chhung thil awm tinreng, awm tan nil eh tawp ni nei tura siamtu chu Krista a ni a, a thil siamten a siamtu chu thil siam chhungah khung luh phet kan tum thin. Thutphaha hmang a, lei ke nghahchhana hmangtu chu a thil siam chhungah a lo kal a ni si a. Tunah erawh chuan a thil siam chu a siamtu chhungah a awm zawk tih hriain awm tan nil eh tawp ni nei tur hringnun ram leh chenna khawvel chu rinna lo ralin awm tan nil eh tawp ni nei lo, chatuanah kan thangharh a, leilung pian hmaa Pathian chatuan remruatah awm tan nil eh tawp ni nei lei Eden leh hunbi chhiar Kristaah a tawp daih tawh si a. Chu ngei chu mi thianghlimte chenna ram, rauthlaa kan luah ram, Thawhlehna nun neitu thlarauva an luah tak chu a ni. Kan thil tih angte hi nil ova, ama remruatna ang zawka leilung pian hmaa min buatsaihsak diam tawh a Isua chu a fapa Isua Kristaah a rawn puang  (inlar) a ni si a (2Tim. 1:10) Kros-a a lei taksa tihborala (tihhluma) awm chuan lei hmasa boral leh tur tih boralna chu a lantir a, a thawhlehna chuan chatuanah Thlarauvin min hruai tawh si a.
                   Chumi avang chuan tun achinah hian keini zawngin tisa lamah chuan tumah kan hre tawh loving; tisaah Krista chu lo hre tawh mah ila, tunah zawng kan hre leh tawh lo ve. Chumi avang chuan tupawh Kristaa a awm chuan thil siam thar a lo ni a, thil hluite chu a ral ta a; ngai teh u, a lo thar ta (2Kor. 5:17). Tisaa Krista hriatna te, tisaa kan lo inhriat dan te hi zawng chatuan ram (Thlarau khawvel) a ni hauh si lova. Sam ziaktu chuan “Pathian ka hre reng a, ka buai thin: Ka kut hi zanah pawh ka la thla ngai lo, ka nun hian thlamuan a duh lova, ka ngaihtuah a, ka thlarau hi a chau thin,” (Sam 77) tiin a sawi a. Lalpa kan lo hriatrengna te, tisaa mi dangte kan lo hriatna te hian kan thlarau ngei chu tichauvin, kan mangang leh thin. Chuti nil ova Lalpan Kristaa min lo hriatna zawkah kan thanharh hnu chuan: Keimah hi Thawhlehna leh nunna (Chatuan ram luahna chu ka ni titu zawk) chu ka ni titu-ah zet chuan tisaa kan hriatna leh mi dangte kan hriatna lamah thiin Krista lamah kan  thangharh phawng mai a, chatuan atan Lalpan min chawlhtirin kan thlarau pawh a hlim ta et et mai a nih hi! Chu velah chuan: ‘In thi tawh a, in nunna chu Pathianah chuan Krista hnenah thuhrukin a awm si a,’ tih te, ‘A nungate chu anmahni lamah an thih a, an thih aia thia tho leha lamah an nun tawh zawkna turin,’ tih te, ‘Thil hlui te chu an ral ta, ngai teh u, a lo thar ta!’ tih te chu Paula chan leh Paula hnena thleng chauh ni lovin kan Testimony a lo ni ve ta a. Krista hnenah khenbehin (Kristaah zawk awmin) ka awm ta, nimahsela ka nung a ni, keimah erawh chu ka ni tawh lo, Krista chu keimahah hian a lo nung ta zawk a ni,’ tih thu te chuan min chhiar chho ta tuar tuar mai a. Bible thu chhiar liam mai mai tawh lovin, a Bible thu ngei chuan kan rilrua a thu pek dah leh kan thinlung pheka ziak zawk chu min chhiarsak ta zawk a ni. 

                     Keimah hi kawng leh thutak leh nuna chu ka ni titu ngei chu kan tan kawng dang rek chawp hauh lova kan kawng, mahniin kalna dung rek lo leh mahnia kal hauh lova min lo kaltir tawhna zawk a lo ni a.
                     Amah ngei bawk chu thutak, a tak thu, keini thu dang tih tak chawp ngai hauh lova min hrilh leh min chantu a ni a. Amah ngai bawk chu nun danga nun tum ngai hauh lova, nunna min lo pek diam tawh chu a ni ngei si a. Kan kawng dik tak chuan chatuan ram chu min lo zawh thlensak tawh a. Chutiang bawkin thihna chu a ni. Chu ngei chu alawm mahni hun theuh zeal kan thawhlehna chu ni. (1Kor. 15:23) Mitthi zing ata piang hmasa berah kan tho ta. Chu thutak zawk chu min kawhhmuh a nih miau avangin: “Tinungtu chu thlarau a ni, nunna pawh a ni” (Jor. Tia a sawi6:63) tia a sawi ni. He thu mai hi chu a chiartu tan thihna a ni a, he thu hi tisa thu ni lovin, thlarau thu chu a sawi a ni si a. Tisaa chan leh nih chawp i tumna kha tawpsan la, nangmaha tumtu tisa chu thihsanin thlarauvah chu thawhlehna ram chu i thleng der a ni ang. Pathian ram chu thu-ah a awm lova, thiltihtheihnaah (Thlarauah Thuin a kawh hmuhah) a awm zawk a ni (1Kor. 4:20). Lehkha thu mai chuan a tihlum si thin a, thlarau erawh chuan a tinung thin a ni (2Kor. 3:6).
                      Nichina kan sawi tawh mi fing chhut thiamte khan thil ropui (lri lam thilah) tak tak an siam chhuak ngei tak a. Chungte chu ngaihsana hlut loh rual pawh a ni lo reng mai. Nimahsela chung thil ngaihtuah theihna thluak siam chhuaktu chuan mi a ber pawhin kan hriatthiam theih turin chatuan ro hlu Krista chu kan chhut buai ngai lovin a pekin min pe tawp mai a, chu ngei chu Pathian khawngaihna thil thlawn pek chu a ni. Tu-in nge lawmthu sawi thiam ta ang le! A chhut ril apiang tan he chatuan atana Pathian remruat hi a ril tulh tulh a, a tawpah chuan mi mawl leh mi a mai an nih chu chatuan remruatna engah chuan an hmu chhuak thin. Chuvangin miten an chatuan nunna thu maia an sawi thiam loh chu khuangte leh Lamin an awi a. Chutiang taka Lalpa faktute tihdan chu ‘mi mawl tihdan’ lo ti thla ngawtute hian finna thuruk hre tura mi a mai kan lo nihzia hi kan la inhmu chhuak lo zawk a ni pal hang tih a hlauhthawnawam hle (Isaia 5:21). 
                   Kros thu chub oral mekte tan atna,
                   Keini chhandam mekte tan erawh chuan
                   Pathian thiltihtheihna a ni si a (1Kor. 1:8)
                   Mi fing finna tihboral a, remhre rem hriatna Pathianin a paih thlakna thuchah engah hian i la fing ngam cheu dawn em ni? Lei leh van reng pawhin an dawl zawh loh tur Krista chuan i tan hunt ha ‘Khawngaihna hun’ a hawn laic he hian i ngaih dan Pathianin, Pathian thu hi tan chhanah lek fang hian i lo la hmang dahrul ang e. Mi tin ta tur tia puan hi nakin lawkah chuan a ni dawn lo. Kohte chu tam tak thlante chu tlemte an ni dawn tlat. Thlan tlakin nangma lamah i chhe ve tawh em?
                   Chatuan Pa-in chatuan nunna min pek avangin chatuan daih lo reng reng hi a chuai hmasa vek phawt a. Amahah chuan a thar hlakin a lo inhre chhuak a ni. Mosian Pharoa Fanua Faa vuah duh lova, rei lo atana sual nawmna hlimpui aia Pathian mite nena tihduhdah tuar a thlan zawkna chhan pawh hi chu chatuan nunna chu a thlang ta a ni. Chutiang taka chatuan nunna Krista hi chatuan rilru pua thlangtute lo chuan a hlutna an hmu phak lo. Chu chatuan nunna Krista Thlarau Thianghlim chu thil dang zawng zawng aia thlangtuteah chauh a inpuang thin. Chatuan nunna neituteah chuan lei lam thil tinreng pawh hi an hlutna dik tak bakin an hlu thei lova, an tlawm thei bawk hek lo. Engkim ama siam a nih angin a siamtu siam chhan ang taka hman a ni. Leilung leh a chhunga thil awm zawng zawng hi Lalpa ta a ni si a. Nangmah neitu-ah i thanngharh ve taw hem le?
                   Tho leh fate chu chatuan nunna Thlarau Thianghlim chuan an pumin an neih zawng zawng nen a pumbilh vangin a vawng thianghlim a, khawvel bawlhhlawh kai lovin a siam thin. An Lalpain tlawmna nuna Setana Kros-a a hneh ang khan, tlawmnain khawvel hi a rochung tawh a ni. Chu tlawmna nun (Kros daihlimah chuan) nunna tui a luang reng si a. Pathian thu awih bawiha an chen avangin Pathian chu hmuh theih loh chuan a thu a, lang theia rinawmna mai ni lovin lang thei lovah an rinawm hlei hlei a ni. Pathian chungnung bera chu a danglam ngai lo angin tho leh fa chu khawvel mite hmaah a tawngtai ngai lo (Mihring hmaah thiamthu sawiin a dikna a chuh ngai lo). Pathian a rin tlak angin a ringtu pawh a rin tlak a ni. Mi tam tak chuan Pathian thu hi dikin a ring a, nimahsela an awih duh chuang lo. Pathian thu awihtu chu ringtu dik tak a ni a, awih lotu hriat phak loh tam tak a hria a ni. Khawvel mi chuan mita a hmuh theih chauh a ring phak a, Pathian fa erawh chuan hmuh theih loh thil thuruk chu a nunna a ni. Chutiang mi chuan Krista chu nun nan a hmang reng a, thih nan pawh a thlang zek zek a ni. Kan nun pawhin kan thih pawhin ama ta kan ni tih ziak ang khan (Rom 14:8). Chutiang mi lungawina chu tih chi-ai rual a ni lo angin, retheih phah nan pawh a Lalpa chu a thlang a, sawi chhiatna leh mualphona tinreng pawh a Lalpa vang chuan a thlum a ni. Krista tana thih ngam lotu chu Krista tan a lo nung lo a ni. Krista tana thih ngam ai chuan nun chu a harsa hle zawk si a. Inthwina nunga inhlan hi thil namen a ni lova, Thlarau Thianghlim zara thinlung thar putute chauhvin chu thih nun chu an nei a ni. An ram chu he khawvel ami a nih miau loh avangin. He hringnun khawvela Pathian ram din duhtu leh zawngtu chuan a pum bak a Pathian phak si lo va. Kros thu pawh hrehawm an tawrh loh nan chauh an chhuang der a ni. Chung mite chu Zawlnei der leh thuhriltu der Kros hmelma an ni si a.
                 Krista Pathian fapa ngei chu tawrhna leh thihna thlangin ropuinaah a lut a. A thihnaa thi vet e a nunnaah kaihthawhin an awm. A tawrhna tuarpui (chanpui) tuten a rorelnaah ro an rel. Krista tawrhna te, thihna te, leh ropuina zawng zawng chu mihring vanga thleng a ni. Ani chuan mihring chu Pathian siam chhan ang taka awm turin chung thil zawng zawng chu a ti a ni. Pathian siam chhan tling loa mihring siamtu zawng zawng chu a bo a bang awm miah lovin a la kiang a ni. Isua Krista thihna ngei chuan mihring chu a sualna te, chak lohna te, sual saltang a nihna te, leh a lungngaihna phurh zawng zawng tunah leh chatuan atan a lak bosak a, ropuina leilung pian hmaa a pek diam tawh chu a khumtir leh ta vah a ni. Kan Lalpa leh Chhandamtu Isua Krista hnathmun zawng zawng chuan mihring tlu chhe tawh chu a dinhmun dik takah a hlang lut fel hmiah a ni si a. Chuvangin Setana han khawih chhiat phak rual kan ni tawh lo va, a va ropui em!    Hla phuahtuin:-
          Aw thawhlehna ni ropui thihna hnehtu,
          Khaw thianghlim ah chuan min thlen la,
          Luikam mawi zawkah chuan,
          Buai leh thihna hnehin ka zai ang e, ti a a phuah chu kan lo thleng reng tawh a lo ni e. Buai leh thihna (Setana leh a hnathawh) hnehin thawhlehna ni ropui thihna hnehtu (Krista)-ah hnehtute kan zai ta. Hla ropui fakna hla mawi chuan:-
           Tholeh fate’n a tui thianghlim,
           Chatuanin an in tawh ang;
            Beram no nunna thianghlimin, 
            Chhandamte an inchawm ang.
            Eden thil hlui awm tawh lovin,
            Nun tharin an leng fo vang.
ti a a saw chu tunah hian kan thleng reng tawh. Taksa thawhlehna a la thlen loh vangin i lo buai ang e, hei hi rah hmasa thu a ni si a. Chu thawhlehna changtute chuan taksa thawhlehna chu an sin nghal dawn si a, taksa tlanna ni, mi thianghlim lawr hunah chuan he thu tak dotute zirtirna chu Pharisai dawidim a ni tih hria ang che. A Pharisai nih leh a dawidim eitu chu thuhmun reng an ni.
            Tho keh fate’n a tui thianghlim (Thlarau Thianghlim) Sacrament tak chu chatuanin kan lo nit a. Beram no nunna thianghlimin chhandamte kan inchawm a, Eden thil hlui (Mihring hlui hringnun khawvel) sualpu taksa, thihna tel tawh lovin, nun tharin kan leng ta e. Rorelna chu Pathian chhungteah tan a ni ta. Chu rorelnaa lute chu kum sang Lal ram (Ring lotute bumtu Setana phuar a nih tikah)-ah kan lut ang. Chu hun thar, Krista lo kal lehna ni atan chuan, chatuan tlang chhipah dingin, tawtawrawt ri danglam tak zion tlang, Thlarauva a tlang thianghlimah a lo ri ta a nih hi (Joela 2:1-11). Tuna tho lova nakina thawhtute’n an thawhlehna Krista chu an hai mek a ni. Amah Lalpa chu a ke nghahchhan khawvel pum pui ai chuan a lian zawk a, he leihringnun te reuhte hian a hliah a ni. I lei mit chhing la, i thinlung mit meng rawh.
