KEI HI THAWHLEHNA LEH NUNNA CHU KA NI - LAL ISUA KRISTA (JOHANA 11:25).
             He thlarauva thawhlehna ram hi ringtu thlarauva piang  apiang tan luah theih vek a ni a. A luah dan kawng hi ngun zawkin i han sawi nawn leh teh ang.
              Prince Charles-a chu Lal chhunghuaah a lo piang a. Nimahsela a pian trih chuan tuna a dinhmun Lallukhum a khumna hi a la hre phak hauh lo. Chutiang bawkin Pathian faa kan lo pianin kan luah tur ram zawng zawng chu vawi-leh khatah kan hrethiam vek lo va. Hunin a rawn keu anng zelin nunna nei tawh  te hnenah a thar zeal rahbi thar pekin kan awm.
             Prince Charles-a chu naupang kum ¾ vel a lo tlin chuan England lal fapa a nihna kawngah chuan a chiang chho zel a. A nu leh pa vanga chu dinhmun chu chang a ni tih pawh a hre chiang ngei ang. Nimahsela Lal a nihna tur leh a Lalzia tur zawng zawng chu hrilhtute vang chauhvin a hre thei a, chu dinhmun chu a thut hma zawng chuan a la chen pha chuang lo. Chutiang bawkin kan pianna avanga kan la luah tur zawng zawng chu kan thlir a, chhuhsak theih rual lohva kan chan vo dik tak a nihna chu Pathian thu hriltute hnenah Thlarau Thianghlim hriattirna thupuan a rahbi te anga kan hnena hriattirna chuan hun thar zelah kan dinhmun thar chu kan chang chho zel a ni.
