             BAPTISMA AWMZIA:- Baptisma hi Greek tawng atanga lak a ni. A hman dan azira awmze hrang hrang nei thei a ni a. Tui Baptisma thu-ah chuan- Hnim, Chiah, Leih, Thlawr, Theh, tihna a ni thei vek.
              Zawlnei Isaia bung 40-a a sawi, Thlarau autu rawl Lalpa kawng lo buatsaihtu, Baptist-tu Johana chuan sual simna Baptisma-in Jordan luiah Jeresulam khuaa mite, Judai rama mi zawng zawngte, Jordan lui dung vela mi zawng zawngte chu a Baptis a. Chu Jordan lui ngeiah chuan khawvel chhandamtu pawhin tuia Baptisma Johana kutah a chang (Mt. 3:5-6; Mt. 3:13-15). Tin, Thuthlung Thar hunah Penticost ni ngei pawhin Peter ate Sermon ropui tak chu Thlarau Thianghlimin a hmang a, mi sangthum lain Isua an ring a, Baptisma chu an chang ta tih kan hria (Tt. 2:41).
                 Johana Baptisma chu heng bung leh changah te hian a hmuh theih: Mt. 3:6; 11-15; Mk.1:14-5,8; Lk.3;3,7,16; Jn. 1:25,31-33; Jn 3:23; Tt. 1:5; Tt. 13:24; Tt. 13:25; Tt. 19:3-4.
                Isuan baptisma a channa heng bung leh changah te hian a lang bawk a: Mt. 3:13-17; Mk. 1:9-11; Lk. 3:21-22.
                 Kristan-ten baptisma an channa heng bung leh chanah te hian a hmuh theih: Mt. 28:19; Tt. 2:38,41; Tt. 8:12,13,16,36,38; Tt.10:47:48; IKor. 10:2; IKor. 12:13; Gal. 3:27; Kol. 2:12; IPet. 3:21.
                 A chunga kan han tarlan tak zawng zawngte khi chhung lama a tak thlengin, a rah chhuah a tak hlimthla chhandam nana ngaitute vawiin nia Setana bumna hmanraw pawimawh berte zinga mi, ngaihthatna pe thei mihring thinlunga bet tlat a ni. Chhung lama a tak (reality) chang si lova mi tan tak ngainahthatna dik lo hulhuala hun luhna hmanruaah Setanan a hman tak avangin Chhandamna atan hriltute chu Kros hmelma, inthendarhna leh pawl siamtu; chhandam nana Tha dang hriltute an nih avangin, hre reng chunga ti an nih phei chuan anchhedawngin an awm ang (Gal. 1:8) tih a hlauhthawnawm hle zawk a ni (IKor. 2:2).
                 Zawlnei Isaia lehkhabu bung 34:16-ah chuan, “Lalpa lehkhabuah zawng ula, chhiar rawh u: chung zingah chuan pakhatmah kawppui nei lo a awm lo vang a, pakhatmah kim lo a awm lo vang: ka ka ngeiin thu a pe a, a thlarau ngeiin chung chu a hruaikhawm ta hlawm si a,” tia a sawi angin, tuia baptisma kawppui atak chu kan aiawha Krista thihna leh thawhlehna chu a ni a, chu thihna leh thawhlehna chu thlarau thianghlim baptisma chu a ni (I kor 6:10-11) “keini zingah Krista isuaa baptisma chang apiangte chu a thihnaah baptis-in kan wm tih in hre lo emaw ni? Chuvangin, a thihnaah baptisma kan chanin, a hnena phum vein kan awm; pa ropuinain mitthi zing ata Krista a kaihthawh ang khan, keini pawh nunna tharin kana wm theih nan,” (rom.6:3-4)  “Krista chuan baptis turin min tir si lo, chanchin tha hril turin mi tir zawk a ni; thufinga hril lovin, chutilochuan Krista kros chu engmah lovah an chanter dah ang e,” (I kor.1:17). Mi tupawh tuiah leh thlarauva an pian loh chuan pathian ram an hmu thei lovang titu ngei zawk chu tuiah leh thlarauva kan pianna thar ani tih (Ijoh. 5:6-8 ah) sawiin. “hemi hi a ni, tui leh thisena lo kala chu, isua Krista hi tui chauhvah ni lovin, tuiah leh thisenah a ni zawk a. Hriattirtu chu thlarau ani, thlarau chu thu tak a nih avangin. Hriattirtu chu pathum an awm, thlarau leh tui leh thisen te chu; chung pathum chu an inthurual a ni,” tiin. Krista thihna chuan diabola hnathawh chu a tihlum a, a thawhlehna chuan ringtu chungah nunna thar Thlarau Thianghlim chu a pe a ni. Chuvangin baptisma tak tak chu chhungril lama Thlarau Thianghlim hnathawh Kros hnehna zara thin lung thar peka kan awmna chu a ni. (Mt. 3:11-12; Mk. 1:8;Lk. 3:16; jn. 1:33; Tt. 1:8; Jn. 16:12-14; Gal. 1:8).
Chuvangin thiltih thi, Krista thu bul hi chhandamna a ni lo tih hria ang chU (Heb. 6:1-3).  Chhandamten pawn lam chhinchhiahna hmuh theihin hmuh theih lohva an chan chhunglam thuruk chu khawvel hnena an puanchhuahna mei a ni. Tuia baptisma hi chhandamna emaw i ti a nih ngat chuan chhandam nana Sabbath (ni bi) serhtu nen thuhmun, thil tiha chhandam tum khawngaihna hre lo hulhual a ni mai. Beram chu beram a nih tawh miau avangin berama chanter i tum chuan i intibuai thlawn a. Pen hi pen nih heantir i tum chuan nangmah leh nangmah i intibuai thlawn mai ang. Mahni Birth Day present lei tum ang maia Pathian khawngaihna, chhandamna kim chu belhchhah a ngai mawlh lova Krista thihna leh thawhlehna chuan sual thuk ber pawh a chhandam zo tih hi hril mai rawh. Lalpa tihlawm tum tawh suh, i tihlawm zawh loh Pathian chuan a lawman kim Krista chu a pe che a, inthawi a hun tawh lo, kan inthawina beram no chu an talh tawh a, chuvangin i kut ang u. Chatuan lawman kim chu Kros lerah a lo lang mi sual tan (Lk. 23:43). Chuvangin chung lama Krista nana inhmangaih rawnna damna erawh chu a ni lo.
SACRAMEN: acramen chungchang thu pawh hi kohhran chanchin kal tawh leh tun hun thlengin sawi dangrang hrang a tam hle. A paw ber thin chu inpumkhatna tura pek, inthen darhna hmanruaa mihring ten kan hmang thin hi a ni. He lehkhabu hian amah Pathian remruatna Krista-a engkim fawk khawm tur daltute ngaih dan that a nih rual rualin sacramen taka min hruai luh a tum a ni.
        Sacramen awmzia: Rom sawrkar ropuui vanglaiin an ram roreltu lal ber Emperor chu an ram chhung chauh ni lovin, khawvel pumah a ropui a ni. Chu an Emperor hmaah chuan Rom sipai tinte chuan chhechhamna leh intiamkamna an nei thin, hetiangin: “Nang hi ka Lalpa i ni. I nunna leh khua leh tui humhim turin, ka taksa leh rilru leh thlarau zawng zawng ka hlan e,” tiin Chutianga an inpekna chu nemnghet turin an kut vei lam zungpuiin au hming zawnah an nem hnam thin a. Chu chu Sacramen leh Thump impression lo chhuahna a ni. Chutiang taka an inpekna a thuk avang chuan Rom sipai Discipline tluka tha sipai inthununnaah a la awm lo hiala rin a ni.
          Chutih hun lal chuan lei leh van lalber Lal Isua chuan he leiah hian hmangaihnain a ram a rawn din a. Chu a ram dinna tur atana thlan chhuah Zirtir-12 te hnenah a taksa leh thisen khawvel hnena a pek tur chu chhang (Wine) hmangin a sem a. Chhandantun a taksa leh thawhlehna ngei chu amah ringtute chanvo liau liau a nih khawvel hnena hmuh theih entirna hmanga a lan chhuahtirna hmasa ber a ni. Thu tisaa lo chang, Thuthlung Hluia a hlimthla rawngbawlna zawng zawngte tihfamkimna Kalvari tlang Kros-a lo la thleng tur chu a tana nun pe ve tur a zirtirte hnenah chuan hmuh theih entir rawngbawlna a hmang a ni (Heb. 1:1-2). Chuvangin Sacramen awmzia diktak chu ringtute inpumpekna “Nang chauh hi ka Lalpa leh ka Pathian i ni, ka taksa leh rilru leh ka thlarau zawang zawng i hnenah ka hlan e,” tihna a ni. Ringtute tana Lal Isua inpumpekna leh ringtute an Lalpa tana inpumpekna, PUMKHAT an nihzia khawvel hnenah puan chhuahna a ni.
           HRIATRENGNA:- Hei hi kan Lalpa Isuan a tisa put lai nia a zirtirte hnena a thu chah a ni. Hetih hun lai hian thinlung lama Thlarau Thianghlim chenchilna nihringteah a la awm loh avangin, “Min hriat rengnan hei hi ti rawh u,”(Lk. 22:19) tiin. Kan nu leh pate thi chu, min hmangaihtu an nih avangin, anmahni hriatrengna atan lung kan phun thin. Kan lung phun avanga hr eta reng kan ni lo va, kan hriatrengna avanga lungphun kan ni. Chuvangin “HRIAT RENG NAN LUNGPHUN” kan ti ngai lo va. Hriatrengna lung kan phun zawk a ni. Kan nupui fanaute pawh kan hriatreng avangin an mamawh thuamhnaw kan leisak thin. Tunge nupui fanau hriatreng nana chung thil chu ti thin le. (This do in remembrance of me:- Min hriatrengna hei hi ti rawh u).
          Isuan a duh ber chu amah hriatreng chu a ni. Hrtih hun lai hian thinlung lama Thlarau Thianghlim chenchilhna mihringteah a la awm loh avangin, “Min hriatrengna hei hi ti r’u,” tiin a taksa kan aia pek tur, a thisen kan sualte tlenfaina atana luang chhuak tur entir nan chhang leh wine a kawhhmuh a ni. Isuan “Ka hrilh a che u, Hei hi Pathian rama atak tak a nih hma loh zawng, ka ei leh tawh dawn lo a ni, (For I tell you, I will never eat it until it is given its full meaning in the Kingdom of God. GNB),” (Lk. 22:16) a tizia a. A khawvel taksa na thei, lungngai thei, thi thei rum thei chu kan tan Kros-a khenbehna a awm a, phuma a awm a, chu thihna thlan chu hneh zo veka a thawhlehna ngei chuan amah kan hriatreng theihna tur Thlarau Thianghlim (Krista Thlarau) chu a kawhhmuh a ni. An chenna khawvel kha an tan mitthi khua ang tluka tihbalawm a ni ngei dawn tih leh tihduhna leh endawngna karah hnutchhiahin a kalsa rih dawn tih a hre reng si a.
          Tichuan thihna rapthlak tak chu tleitla a, hnehna hlado a chham fel hnuah a thlarau a thlah ta a. A tuk thum tukah ThlarauThianghlim chuan thihna ata a kai tho leh a, mitthi zing ata piang hmasa tur (Thup. 1:5) chu a zirtir hnenah vawi tam tak inlarin Thlarau Thianghlim lo thleng tur chu a tiam fel hnuah (Tt. 1:4-8) vanah a lawnsan ta a. A hrilh lawk ang ngeiin Penticost ni ropui takah chuan Pa thil tiam chu zirtirten an lo chang ta (Tt. 2:3-4). Zawlnei Joelan a lo sawi lawk chu a lo thleng ta, khawvel hneh loh nun an nei ta. An Lalpa chu an nun chhungrilah a lo cheng ta (Tt. 2:4). Sacramen tak Baptisma tak chu an chang ta. Fa nihna an changing, kan chang ta (Rom :14-17; IJoh. 3:1). A hlimthla a chuai ta. Ni thimah changing, thla thisenah a chang ta. Pathian ram chu kan kawchhungah a awm ta (2Kor. 6:16-18). Pathian chhungte nen thlarauvah kan lengza ta. Van khua leh tui kan lo nit a (Eph. 2;19-22) Tlang khawih theih lohah kan cheng ta (Heb. 12:18-24). Van atangin Krista lo kal lehna chu kan nghak ta a nih hi (Ph. 3:20). Ama ruala min kaithawh avang leh mahni hun theuh zeal thawh hmahruaituah kan thawh tawh avangin (IKor. 15:22-25). Chuvangin Sacramen tak chu Thlarau Thianghlima Krista taksa leh thisen ei leh in (Thutak zawng zawnga hruai luha awmna) chu a ni e. Kan chhang leh Uain hmanga Sacramen sem chu hmangaihna avanga tih a nih chuan a tha a. Chhandamnaa ngaitu tan chuan bumna thang a ni. Sem loh hmak ngamtu chuan a tak a hria a ni. Pawl siamtu lek a nih avangin.
SABBATH:- Sabbath hi Pathianin Mosia hmanga mihringte hnena a pek, Sinai tlang Dan 10 zinga pakhat a ni (Ex. 20:8-11).
     Sabbath awmzia:- Sabbath awmzia chu- Chawlhna hmun emaw Chawlhna ni emaw tihna a ni. Pathianin ni ruk chhungin Lei leh Van a siam a, a ni sarih niin a chawl a, chu chawlhna ni chu a hnam thlan Israel-te tan an kar khat chhung kut hna thawh zawng zawngte chawlhsan chu ni chu chawlh nana hmang tur leh serh thianghlim ttturin thupek (Dan) angin a pe a ni. An ran vulhte thleng pawhin chu ni ropui tak chu chawlhna ni atan an hmang ngei ngei tur a ni (Ex. 20:8-11).
     A pek chhan:- ‘Keimah leh Israela thlahte inkarah hian kumkhuaa thuthlun chhinchhiahna a ni” (Ex. 31:17) “Chu lo chu kei leh anmahni inkara chhinchhiah nan ka chawlhnite chu anmahni ka pe a, kei hi Lalpa, anmahni serh hrangtu ka ni tih an hriat theih nan,” (Eze. 20:12). “Ka chawlhnite serh ula, kei leh nangni inkara chhinchhiahna a ni ang a, Lalpa in Pathian chu ka ni tih in hriat theihna a ni dawn nia,” (Eze. 20:20).
      Sabbath tak:- Sabbath chu chawlhna ni a ni angin a kawppui ringtute chawlhna ni chu Krista a ni. Chu Krista chu a lo lan hma zawng chuan lei ni hunbbi khawchhak atanga lo lang thin ni (Sun) hmanga chhiar ni sarihna chu an hmangin an serh thianghlim ngei tur a ni, a tak Krista chu Israelte chauh ni lo khawvel chhandam tura leia alo lan dawn avangin. Chu Lal Isua khawvel chhandamtu lo kalna hmsa lo thlenna chu an hmuah dik theih nan Zawlnei Isaia lehkhabuah chuan, “Rorel zawm ula, felt akin ti rawh u: ka chhandamna chu a lo thleng dawn dawnin, ka felna chu a lo lang dawn dawn ta si a. Chutiang ti mi leh, chu mi pawm tlattu mihring fapa chu, a eng a thawl e; chawlhni bawhchhe lova serh thinntu leh, thil tha lo reng reng ti lo tura a kut veng tha thintu chu (Is. 56:1,2) tiin. Mesia lo kal tur an nghahhlelh em em chu an hail oh nan Israela thlahte hnena chhinchhiahna pek chu Sabbath a ni. Chu Mesia (Krista) chu a lo kal ta ngei a, nimahsela an hai tlat si. Chawlhni lal a nihna te leh chawlhni chu mihring tana siam a ni a, mihring hi chawlhni tana siam a ni lo ti tein amah chu an hriat chhuah theihna tur kawng hrang hrang a sawiin thiltihin a lantir a (Mar. 2:28; Matt. 12:12). Israel fate ang bawkin vawiin thleng hian chawlhna Krista haitute chuan a ni bi-ah tihdik tumin chu Dan bawiah chuan Dan chungah Dan chherchhuanin anmahni an intitang a ni. Sabbath kawppui Krista, a tak chu an la hai cheu avangin. Bawi ni lo turin Krista chuan min chhuahtir kha, chutichuan ding nghet u la (a takah chuan chaw u la), bawi nghawngkawlah chuan tang leh tawh suh u (Gal. 5:1). Chutichuan ei thu-ah emaw, in thu-ah emaw, kut ni, a thu-ah emaw, thla thar thu-ah emaw, chawlhni (Sabbath) thu-ah emaw tuman sawisel che u suh se; chung chu thil lo thleng turte hlim a ni, a tak erawh chu Krista ta (Thlarau Thianghlim) a ni (Kol. 2:16-17). Pathian, hmasanga thlahtute hnena bung tam tak leh kawng tinrenga Zawlneitea thu lo sawitu khan, heng ni tawpah hian keimahni hnenah a Fapaah chuan thu a sawi ta” (Heb. 1:1-2). Zawlnei Joela hmanga Pathianin a lo puan tawh chu Krista hnehna zarah chuan Pentticost ni-ah a lo thleng a, NI (NI bi-a biakna) thimah a chang (a tawp) a, thla (Moon) (biakna) thisenah a chang ta (Joela. 2:28-32; Tt. 2:17-21; Ez. 8:16). Ni tak Kristaah kana wm ta (2Thes. 5 : 8)- Josua chuan anni ho chu a chawlhtir tawh si zawngin chumi hnuah ni dang thu chu a sawi lo vang. Chuitichuan, Pathian mite tan chuan chawlhnia chawlhna a la awm ta f o va. A chawlhnaa lit tawh chu, Pathianin ama hnathawhte a chawlhsan ang khang, chumi pawh chuan a hnathawhte a chawlhsan ve ta a (Heb 4: 8- 10). He lei ni bi hman laia an lo serhte kha a la awm lai ngei (Thawhtan –Inrinni) hian a takah ringtute an chael der tawh tih thu min hrilh a ni. Chuvangin Sabbath emaw Sunday emaw serh hian awmzia pakhat mah a nei lo va, chawlhni Kristaa chawlte tan chuan ni tin hi ang khat vek Lalpa nena inpawlna atana pek zawk  kan ta ani e. Chuvangin ni 1000 hini khat Krista a ni a. Ni chhiar sen loh chatuan ni Kristaah kan leng tawh si a.  Chhun leh Zan reng aawm lo kan lenna Zion ni eng hnuaiah hian thawh rah sengtuten chu nun chu an hre phak lo, chawlhna rah sengtuten ei sen loh an thar reng thung. Chu chawlhnaa lut tur chuan a zemah i lut ang u. Kar khat chhunga ni khat emaw Lalpa biak nana hman bik hi chhungkua leh vantlang tan a tha a. Serh tur erawh chu a ni lo. 
 THLARAU THIL PEK :- Isua Krista taksa  ropuina chu thlarau thil pek chi hrang hrangte chhuahna pakhat a nihna chu a ni.  Chungte chu an zavaia that tlanna tura lo awm a nih avangin.  
              THLARAU THIL PEK CHI 9 TE:-  
Finna (a message full of wisdom).
Hriatna (a message full of knowledge).
Rinna (Faith).
Tihdam theihna (The power of heal).
Thil mak tih theihna (The power to work miracles).
Thu hrilh theihna (The gift of speaking God’s message).
Thlarau hriat dik theihna (The ability to tell the defference between gifts that comes from the spirit and those that do not).
Tawng chu hrang hranga thu sawi theihna (Tawng hriat loh- The ability to speak in strange tongues).
Tawng hriat lohte hriatfiah theihna (The ability to explain what is said of strange tongues). (Kor. 12:7-11).
       A chunga Thlarau thilpek kan han sawi takte khi, Thlarau hmun khat vek chhuan mi tin hnenah a duh ang zeal sem theuhvin a thawk thin tih kan hmu a. Chuvangin mahni chan chauh en lova mi dangte chan pawh thawl halha lem thei tura Thlarau Thianghlim fate chu zirtir kan ni. Chung zawng zawngte chu kan zavaia Lalpa kan pawl tlan theih nana pek kan nih zawk avangin.
        Nimahsela chung thil hlu tak maite chu bumna hmanga Diabola hi a chet ve reng avangin inpumkhatna aiin inthendarhna hmanruaah a lo chang thin. A chhan chu tute emaw Pathian aia thilpek betu (pathiantu) an awm thin avang leh tisa mi Thlarau thilpek hrethiam reng reng lo tutee maw hmanga verther taka che an awm thin avangin. A ta kan nih min hriattirna chu min petu Pathian aia dah sangtu leh a bera ngaitu an awm veleh Setana chu kawlphe aia rangin a che nghal thin a ni.
        Chuvang tak chuan: Mihring tawngte leh vantirhkoh tawngtein thu sawiin , hrilh theihna neiin thu ruk zawng zawng leh hriatna zawng zaawng hre vekin , tlang sawn theihna khawp hial rinna famkim neiin, mi relheite chawm nan ka sum zawng zawng pe vek mah ila, ka taksa pawh kang turin inpe mah ila, hmangaihna chung zawng zawng hluhlanga siamtu chu ka tlakchham tlat chuan, dar benthek ri leh dar ri mai mai, awmze nei lo leh sawtsawhlawt lo, ka tan lek phei chuan, laipui mu awm lo ka pang lek fang ka lo ni ang. (IKor. 13:1-13) tih hi kan hre kiau a ni.
       Chuvangin tunah hian Jentailte famkimna Thawhlehna Ram thlarauvah kan thlen tawh avangin Thlarau thilpek zawng zawngte pawh mahni lama thawhchhuahpui kan tum vaih chuan a thing her lum ang a ni a. Chutiang bawkin Thuhrilhna te pawh mahni inbuatsaihna leh tawngkam thiamna mai a nih chuanin are k pachal rah pherh ang chauh, a uihin a uih hluah hluah a ni. Eng hunah nge kan din tak? Darthlalanga inhmu riai ruai ram leh hunah kan ding tawh lova, naupang tihdan hi bansan ngama Pathian kan lo vawn dang zawng thlah huamtute Lalpain a au chhuakin chhinchhiahna hun hunhnung berah kan ding ta a nih hi. Pathian Thlarau Thianghlim chuan a hnenah engkim min kawlsakin a ruakin min dah tawh a, a hun teah a thata a rah hunah heng thilpek zawng zawngte hi a fate chu min hnmantir mai zawk a ni. A famkim a lo thlen hunah erawh chuan a kum lo hi tihban a ni taw hang. Englai pawha kan hnena a dah reng chu heng thil pathum hi a ni. Rinna Beiseina leh Hmangaihna, A ropui ber chu hmangaihna hi a ni. Zakaria 4:6 thu Chakna ni lovin, thiltihtheihna ni hek lovin, ka thlarau zawkin le, tiin sipaiho Lalpa chuan kan hnenah a pung a ni.
 Thil nung pali: 
Sakeibaknei ang.
Bawng no ang.
Mihring hmel ang.
Mupui ang.
         Hengte hi Pathian hun bi 4-a (then lia) a inlar chhuah dan thuruk a ni.
         Sakeibaknei ang: Eden tluk hun atanga Nova hun (Tui let) thleng kha a ni a. Mihring sualna chu ngaihdamna tel lovin Pathianin a hrem a, a tiboral vek a ni. Mi 8 Nova-te chhungkua chauh lo chu. 
          Bawng no ang: khawvel hun dang, Nova te chhungkaw hmanga mihring leh thil nung tinreng din chhuah leh hnu-Nova hun atanga Lal Isua lo lan hun hma, Dan anga ran thisen hmanga inthawina hun chu a ni. Mi sualin mi sual tan ran thi chu a hlan a, thi leh thi, anchhedawng hunaia awmte inthawina hun, a tak hlimthla chenna huna Pathian inlarna hun entirna a ni. Hmangaihna tel lovin, Danin a phut angin khawngaihna tel lovin ran thisen inthawi nan an hlan thin a, chu chuan sual a sil fai lo va, a inthawite pawh a tifamkim thei hek lo. Awm rengna a thlen lo va, Lalpa pawhin a hawisan tawh a ni. (Heb. 8:9; Heb. 10:1-17).
          Mihring hmel ang: Pathian mihringa a llo channa. Mihring hmel ang pua Isua lokalna hun chu a sawi a ni. Khawvel sual kalpuitu tur, khawngaih leh thu taka khat Dan leh inthawina tifamkima titawp tura, khawvel chhandamtu mihringte mithmuh ngeia lo lang. Kalvari tlang Kros-a an khenbeh tak chu min kawhhmuh a. Amahah Thuthlung Hlui a ral vek a ni (IKor. 5:8).
          Mupui ang: Lal Isua Krista Chhandamna famkim rawn thlentu chu, thlan hremhmun leh Diabola hmathawh tiborala hneh zovin, thlan ata a tho leh a. Tho leh Krista chuan he lei hi a chhuahsan hun ni 50 velah Penticost ni ngei chuan Thlarau Thianghlim a lo thleng ta a. Chu Thlarau Thianghlim hun chu Penticost ni-a intanin Krista lo kal leh hma zawng chu Mupui anga Pathian inlarna hunah kan ding a ni (Tt. 2:17-21). Tupawh Krista Thlarau nei lo chu lo kal leh tur Krista ta a ni lo va, a ta te hnenah chuan Thlarau Thianghlim chuan an thlarau hnenah Pathian fate an nih puangin Abba! (Ka pa) yiin Isua Krista chu an pa a nihnaah an ko a ni. Thlarau Thianghlim chauh lo chuan lo chuan Isua chu tuman Lalpa an ti thei lo (Ram 8:9-17; IJoh. 3:24; IIKor. 5:5; IIKor. 3:3; Heb. 12:9; Ikor. 12:13).
          Chu hun hnuhnung (ni hnuhnung). Thlarau thianghlim in chu Krista lo kal lehna ni ropui chuan a rawn thlak tep avangin. Zan laiah kan ding ta a. Chu zan lai au aw chu Inralrinna thu a nih tak avangin Pathianin ringtute (Thlarau Thianghlim changtute) kum sang Lal rama seng turin RThlarauva a tlang thianghlimah a hruai lut hmasa a ni. Chu ngei chu Thlarau Thawlehna Ram chu a ni e. Lalpa (Thlarau) ata chu kan hmuh ang zelin tihdanglamin kan awm a ni (IKor. 3:18). Pathian famkimna tinreng tluka tihkhaha awmin keimahni lam kan ruak thung a ni. ‘Thlarau Thianghlima khatin awm rawh u’ tih chu ‘Lo ruak rawh u’ tihna a ni tlat! (Eph. 3:14-19).
          MOTOR TEHKHINNA:- Hun zelin Pathian thuruk chu a rawn keu va, Thlarau Thianghlim chu chu min hhriattir a ni (Lk. 12:54-56). Hun kal tawh zawng zawngah chuan a bung hrang te tein a lo thleng a. A ke a lo thlenin, a khalhna a tel lo va, a khalhna a telin a tui a tel lo va, a tui a awmin a driver a tel lo va, a driver a awmin a in a tel lo va, a in leh a driver a awmin a engine a awm leh lo va. Runah erawh chuan a famkimin Pathian pawlna chu a lo thleng thin a. Amah Pathian ngei chuan a kawng dik takah khalhin kan chuang ho ta dial dial a nih hi. Inbumna kawng tinreng leh bawlhhlawhna zawng zawngte kalsainin Thianghlimna kawngah ringtuten khawvel kan ep tan mek a ni. Sual ngam chein awm suh la, thatnain sual chu nfam zawk rawh (Rom. 12:21).
PATHIAN THU (BIBLE) LEH THLARAU THIANGHLIM
Tun lai hian ringtute zingah Pathian Lehkhabu thu leh Thlarau Thianghlim inlaichhin dan hriat loh vangin he baia kal tam tak an awm a ni. Thenkhatin Pathian Thu hi Thlarau Thianghlim a ni mai. Thlarau Thianghlim hran a awm lo va, beisei tur a ni hek lo tiin an sawi a. Chutiang mite chuan Johana ziak bung 6:63 thu, “Tinungtu chu thlarau a ni, tisa chu engahmah a tlak tlai lo; in hnena thu ka sawite hi thlarau a ni, nunna pawh a ni,” tia Lal Isua thusawi chu tan chhanah an hmang thin. Tin, lehlamin, IIKor. 3:6 thu leh IKor. 4”20 thu, “Amah bawk chuan thuthlung thar rawngbawltuah min tlintir a; a lehkha thu mai rawngbawltuahte ni lovin, a thlarau rawngbawltuahte a ni zawk e; lehkha thu mai chuan a tihlum si thin a, thlarau erawh chuan a tinung thin a ni. Pathian ran chu thuah a awm lo va, thiltihtheihnaah a awm zawk a ni,” tiin.
           Hemi chungchang thuah hian Lal Isua zirtirna fiah tak ma ii zir ang u. Chanchin Tha Luka ziak bung 10:30-35 thuah he lai thuruk hi mawi takin a sawi a ni.
           Tu emaw Jerusalem khua atangin Jeriko khuaah a zuk kal dawn a, suamhmangte a tawk hlauh va, chumi te chuan a silhfen te chu hlihsakin an vaw neka thi lek lekin an kalsan ta a. Puithiam tuemaw leh Levia chi tuemaw chu kawngah chuan lo kalin amah chu an rawn hmu a, kawng sirah an helsan ta mai a. A tawp berah Samari mi tha a lo kal a, chu suamhmang tawk chu a hmuh velah a khawngaih em em a, a pemah te hriak leh wine a hnawihsak a, a tuam a, a enkawl ta a. Tin, a tukah chuan duli pahnih a phawrh a, khualbuk vengtu hnenah a pe a, “Lo enkawl la, hemi baka is en zawng zawng chu ka lo kal leh hunah ka rul le hang che,” a ti a.
          He lai tehkhin thu hi vengte (neighbours) chungchanga Lal Isuan a sawi a ni. Keini tana tangkai tak tur lal Isuan a sawi a ni. Suamhmang tawk chu mihringte hi kan ni a, Suamhmang huatthlala ber chu Setana a ni. Samari mi tha chu Lal Isua a ni. Khualbuk chu he lei hi a ni. He leia kan awm chhung zawnga kan inenkawlna tur leh Krista lo kal leh tur chu kan hmuah theih nan Duli pahnih pek kan ni. Pakhat chu Pathian (Bible) hi a ni a. A dang leh chu Thlarau Thianghlim chu a ni.
          Miin Pathian thu hre hle mahse a taka zawm theihna chu Thlarau Thianghlim zara awm a ni. Thlarau Thianghlim changtute tan Thlarau Thianghlim hruaina dik kan hriat theihna atana eng leh khawnvar chu Bible thu a ni (Sam 119:105).
           Pathian thu hi Thlarau Thianghlim ngunhnam a ni (Ep. 6 :17). 
           Chuvangin thu mai chuan a tihlum thin a, thlarau chuan thu chu a hmanin nunna thu a lo ni thin. 
           Thlarau Thianghlim a hrana awm ring lo hi chuan a Pathian thu pawh a ring thei chuang lo va. Pathian thu ngaisang lotu chuan Thlarau Thianghlim a nei chuang hauh lo. Ringtu dik tak chuan, Pathian thu a ngainain hmuh theih loh Thlarau Thianghlim thiltihtheinaah a rinchhan a ni.
KRISTA LEH KRISTIAN
                   Tunlaiin ringtu intite zingah Isua kan nunna a nih avangin Isua kan ni tih te, Krista chu keimahnia a nun tawh vangin chu nunna Kristaa nung te Krista kan ni tih te, Krista Isua leh ringtu chu pum khat (pakhat) an nih vangin Isua Krista kan ni tihnge, Hringtu leh hrin chu pakhat (eg. Beram chu beramin a hringa beram a ni) chi khat an nih vangin Pathian kan ni tithe a ri ta huai mai. (Tan chhan: John. 10:34,35;  Gal. 2:20;  Sam  2:6)
                    He thil lo chhuahna chhan hi Setana bumna vanga lo awm, Krista leh ringtute inlaichin dan an man thelh vanga lo awm mi tam tak bumna thang hlauhawma tantir  tlattu a ni.  Entirna hmangin lo sawi fiah ila:
                    Thlikthliekbawm hi Hlai kungah te, thingsiaah te a awm thin a. Chu Thlikthleikbawm chuan a awmna Hlai kung nunna chu ringin a nung ve a ni. Amaha nun hran a neih loh avangin a awmna Hlai kung chu lo thi se, a thi ve mai a ni. Chuvangin Thlikthliekbawm nunna chu Hlai nunnachu a ni ve mai. Nimahsela Thlikthliekbawm chuan nun nan Hlai nunna chu a rin avangin Thlikthliekbawm chu Hlai a ni chuang lo. Chutiang bawkin Pathian lama kan nunna chu Krista a ni a. Kan nunna Krista a nih vangin Krista kan ni chuang lo va. Krista ringtu mihring thar kan ni.
              Lal Isuan Kei Grep hrui tak ka ni, nangni a pengte in ni a ti a. Grep peng atangin a kungpui (hruipui) a chhuak ngai lo va, a hruipui atrangin a pengte a lo chhuak thin. Grep pengte an nih avangin Grep chu ni mahse a hruipui an ni chuang lo va. A pengte sah thlak vangin a kungpuiin a thihphah bawk hek lo. A kungpui sah chhum chuanin a pengte pawh an thi thin. Chutiang bawkin Krista pengte kan ni a, ka nunna, chatuan pawha thi thei lo chu nun nan kan ring (a lova nung thei lo) a ni. (Joh. 15:1-8).
     
              Lui pakhat a awm a chu mi pengte chuan Pathian khawpui chu a tilawm thin (Sam 46:4) Chu Lui pakhat chu Krista a ni a, a pengte chu ringtute kan ni (John. 15:1-8).
              Chutichuan Krista i ni lo va, Isua i ni bawk lo va, Pathian pawh i ni hek lo. Amah Pathianah chuan Thlarau Thianghlim zara Krista unau, a chatuan roluahpuitute kan ni. (1John. 3:1); Pathianin a hrina a hrin, Pathian fate, van chhungkua kan ni (Heb. 2:11). 
